Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.71,0:00:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,真實故事改編
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.97,0:00:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,1983年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.99,0:00:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,當你愛一個人，你必須相信他\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: [Voiceover] When you love someone, you've gotta trust them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.41,0:00:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,別無它法\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}There's no other way.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.42,0:00:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你得將掌管生命中一切的那把鑰匙給他\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You've got to give them the key to everything that's yours.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.34,0:01:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,要不然有什麼意義？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Otherwise, what's the point?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.59,0:01:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,一直以來，我深信我擁有的是這樣的愛\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}And, for a while, I believed that's the kind of love I had.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.20,0:03:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,在我開賭場及被炸之前…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Before I ever ran a casino, or got blown up...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.33,0:03:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,艾斯羅斯坦，可是最屌的賽馬預測者\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Ace Rothstein was a hell of a handicapper.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.96,0:03:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我告訴你\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I can tell you that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我旺到每次只要我下注，全國的賭盤賠率…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I was so good that whenever I bet, I'd change the odds...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.46,0:03:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,都會隨著改變\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}for every bookmaker in the country.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.22,0:03:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不蓋你，我對賽馬的研究精湛到…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I'm serious, I had it down so cold...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.76,0:03:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我晉升人間天堂\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}that I was given paradise on Earth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.22,0:03:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我被升為拉斯維加斯最大賭場之一《坦吉樂》的管理人…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I was given one of the biggest casinos in Las Vegas to run, the Tangiers...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.44,0:03:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,唯有聘請我的那幫人才能如此大手筆\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}by the only kind of guys that can actually get you that kind of money.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,六千兩百七十萬美元\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}$62, 700, 000.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道細節\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I don't know all the details.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.15,0:03:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,老實說，沒人知道細節…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: [Voiceover] In fact, nobody knew all the details...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,原本應該很完美的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}but it should've been perfect.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.53,0:03:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他有我這好友尼奇山多羅挺他…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He had me, Nicky Santoro, his best friend, watching his ass...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:03:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他手中也攬著他愛的女人，金吉兒\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}and he had Ginger, the woman he loved, on his arm.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.34,0:04:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,到頭來，我們全搞砸了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}But in the end, we fucked it all up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.13,0:04:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,原本應多完美\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}It should've been so sweet, too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,結果，我們這樣的小混混…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}It turned out to be the last time that street guys like us...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,在這次之後就再也無緣搞油水這麼豐富的大生意了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}were ever given anything that fucking valuable again.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那時的賭城，是蠢蛋們…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Vegas was a place where suckers...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,一毛一毛存足了錢飛來…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}flew in every year on their own nickel...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,直到輸光了家當才走人的地方\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}and left behind about a billion dollars.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,在夜晚，你看不到包圍拉斯維加斯的沙漠\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}But at night, you couldn't see the desert that surrounds Las Vegas.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,但城堻\多的問題卻都是在沙漠婺悃M的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}But it's in the desert where lots of the town's problems are solved.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.46,0:04:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,沙漠堛漣|洞可多著呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: Got a lot of holes in the desert...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.38,0:04:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,堶戛I藏了很多問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}and a lot of problems are buried in those holes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,只是程式要對\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Except you gotta do it right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.30,0:04:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你得先把洞挖好…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You gotta have the hole already dug...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.05,0:04:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,再將貨從汽車後車箱載來\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}before you show up with a package in the trunk.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.51,0:04:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,要不然你就得在沙漠挖上個30到45分鐘\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Otherwise, you're talking about 30 or 45 minutes of digging.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.35,0:04:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,誰又知道期間會有什麼人出現？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Who knows who's gonna be coming along in that time?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不知不覺中，你又得多挖好幾個洞\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Before you know it, you gotta dig a few more holes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,搞不好一整晚都得耗在那兒\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You could be there all fucking night.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.44,0:04:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.45,0:05:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,坦吉樂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.62,0:05:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,精華地段-拉斯維加斯，十年前\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}THE STRIP - LAS VEGAS TEN YEARS EARLIER{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.46,0:05:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,誰抗拒的了？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Who could resist?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.63,0:05:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,在別處，我只是個登記賽馬的一個賭徒…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Anywhere else, I was a bookie, a gambler...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.47,0:05:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,老是得小心翼翼，成天被條子們騷擾\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}always looking over my shoulder, hassled by cops, day and night.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.89,0:05:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但在這兒，我可是羅斯坦先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}But here, I'm Mr. Rothstein.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.93,0:05:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不但不偷雞摸狗，還管間賭場\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I'm not only legitimate, but running a casino.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.68,0:05:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那就像是將夢想換為現金\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}And that's like selling people dreams for cash.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.69,0:05:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我聘任了賭場的一個老朋友 比利雪伯當經理，然後開始工作\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I hired an old casino pal, Billy Sherbert, as my manager, and went to work.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,這是負責牌室的羅尼\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}And this is Ronnie, who takes care of the card room.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.99,0:05:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,像我們這種人 拉斯維加斯洗去了我們的罪孽\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: For guys like me, Las Vegas washes away your sins.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.08,0:05:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,像是道德洗車場一樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}It's like a morality car wash.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.21,0:05:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,它對我們的效用就像法國露德 對駝背和殘障的人一樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}It does for us what Lourdes does for humpbacks and cripples.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.59,0:05:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不但讓我們重見天日…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: And along with making us legit...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.22,0:05:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,還帶來了現金，數不盡的錢\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}comes cash, tons of it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.93,0:06:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不然你以為我們沒事 跑到這沙漠中央幹嘛？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}What do you think we're doing here in the middle of the desert?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.85,0:06:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,就是為了這些錢\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}It's all this money.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.57,0:06:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,這是所有炫目的燈光…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}This is the end result of all the bright lights...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.44,0:06:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的招待、香檳、免費住宿…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}and the comped trips, of all the champagne...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.61,0:06:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,女人與喝不完的酒 最終所造成的結果\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}and free hotel suites, and all the broads and all the booze.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.87,0:06:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,全都是為了 讓我們弄走你的錢\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}It's all been arranged just for us to get your money.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.58,0:06:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是賭城的真面目\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}That's the truth about Las Vegas.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.34,0:06:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我們是唯一的贏家\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}We're the only winners.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.05,0:06:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,賭徒們一點機會都沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}The players don't stand a chance.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.43,0:06:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,而他們的錢從賭桌上…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}And their cash flows from the tables...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.76,0:06:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,流入我們的收銀櫃再進入保險籠…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}to our boxes through the cage...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.47,0:06:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,最後流入全賭場最神聖的房間\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}and into the most sacred room in the casino.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他們計算錢的地方…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}The place where they add up all the money...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.56,0:06:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,注意-請勿進入 萬物之首，計算室\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}the Holy of holies, the count room.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.82,0:06:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,這兒可不是閒雜人等可進出的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Now, this place was off-limits.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.41,0:06:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,連我都進不去\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Even I couldn't get inside.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.87,0:06:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,當然，但我的工作是讓它保持 滿滿的狀態\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}But it was my job to keep it filled with cash. That's for sure.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.91,0:06:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,媕Y的錢多到…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: They had so much money in there...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.08,0:06:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,可讓你用百元大鈔砌棟房子\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}you could build a house out of stacks of $100 bills.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:06:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,最棒的是…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}And the best part was that upstairs...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.59,0:07:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,上頭董事會什麼屁都不知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}the Board of Directors didn't know what the fuck was going on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.71,0:07:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,在他們看來一切都乾淨俐落 沒人動手腳\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}To them everything looked on the up-and-up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.05,0:07:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不是嗎？當然不\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Right? Wrong.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.68,0:07:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,確認五千元\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Verify $5,000.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.97,0:07:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,在計算室的那些人…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: The guys in the counting room...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.01,0:07:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,都是被派進去將媕Y吸幹的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}were all slipped in there to skim the joint dry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.85,0:07:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他們會少算錢，將計單弄掉\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}They'd do short counts, they'd lose fill slips.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.56,0:07:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至直接從箱堮釣垓{款\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}They'd even take cash right out of the drop-boxes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.15,0:07:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,全是靠這傢伙…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}And it was up to this guy right here...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.11,0:07:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,站在兩百萬元前的這位…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}standing in front of $2 million...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.36,0:07:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,在被國稅局或任何人發現前…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}to skim the cash off the top without anybody getting wise...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.74,0:07:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,把錢摸走\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}the IRS or anybody.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.04,0:07:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,在計算室 好像都沒人在看\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Notice how in the count room nobody ever seems to see anything.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.29,0:07:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不知怎的，大家都視若無睹\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Somehow, somebody's always looking the other way.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.63,0:07:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,看看這些傢伙 他們看來真忙，不是嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Look at these guys. They look busy, right?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.00,0:07:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他們在算錢，誰會吵他們呢？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}They're counting money. Who wants to bother them?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.55,0:07:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是，天曉得他們會不會 犯了錯而忘記偷錢\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I mean, God forbid they should make a mistake and forget to steal.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,這期間，你可來去自如\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Meanwhile, you're in and you're out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.81,0:07:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,走過那些鳥事不幹的警衛 每禮拜還多拿一百元…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Past the jag-off guard who gets an extra $100 a week...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.73,0:07:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,只為了看門\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}just to watch the door.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.48,0:07:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,一如往常一樣規律…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}It's routine. Business as usual...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.15,0:07:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,走進、走出、你好、再見\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}in, out, hello, goodbye.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,就這麼簡單\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}That's all there is to it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:08:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,就只是個拎著皮箱 走出賭場的肥豬\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Just another fat fuck walking out of a casino with a suitcase.{\r}
