Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,整個中西部…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}all over the Midwest...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他們都會在這個位於 堪薩斯市的市場碰面\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}and they would meet in this produce market in Kansas City.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.54,0:08:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,根本沒人會知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Nobody even knew it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.71,0:08:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,有一個讓他媽做菜\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}One of the guys made his mother do the cooking.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.96,0:08:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你有看到傑瑞史塔瑞歐嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Do you ever see that guy Jerry Steriano?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.26,0:08:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,這些老頭們看來可能不怎麼樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: These old greaseballs might not look it...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但相信我…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}but believe me...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他們才是賭城的秘密操縱者\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}these are the guys who secretly controlled Las Vegas.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:08:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽，那男人又來了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}WOMAN: Mama, that man's here again.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.97,0:09:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,因為他們控制著 全美卡車司機工會\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: Because they controlled the Teamsters Union.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.44,0:09:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,而要開賭場非得到那兒去借錢\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}And that's where you had to go to borrow money to buy a casino.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.90,0:09:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,-你要放蝦嗎？ -我會的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}WOMAN 2: Would you put in shrimp? WOMAN: I would.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,要是這些傢伙們每月拿不到 這只小箱子…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: Nobody got a Teamsters' loan unless the guys in this room...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.20,0:09:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那誰就都別想貸到款\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}knew they were gonna get their little suitcases.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.83,0:09:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,像這從底特律來的老傢伙\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Guys like this antique over here, out of Detroit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.41,0:09:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,或尤其是像利蒙蓋吉 這群人的首腦\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Or especially guys like Remo Gaggi, the outfit's top boss.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.00,0:09:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,有大概數字嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You got a round figure on it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.38,0:09:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對是這房堻怑垠n的人物\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: Definitely the most important guy in this room.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.59,0:09:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-十公斤，那就差不多七十萬了 -很好\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}FRANK: About 20 pounds. Around $700,000. REMO: Good.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.80,0:09:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,雖說對拉斯維加斯還有點早…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}STONE: It's a little early for Las Vegas...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.47,0:09:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但我想邀請賭博遊樂業界的 先生與小姐們…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}but I want to welcome the ladies and gentlemen of the gaming industry....{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.52,0:09:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,就以世界所知…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: As far as the world was concerned...{\r}
