Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.82,0:09:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是個清白的人物\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}was a legitimate guy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.11,0:09:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,有權力的人\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}A powerful man.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.45,0:09:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他與總統一同打高爾夫\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He played golf with the President.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.28,0:09:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,代表卡車司機工會退休基金會…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}ANDY: On behalf of the Teamsters' Pension Fund...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.54,0:09:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-我很高興將這… -但安迪也聽命於人\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I'm glad to present... SAM: But he also took orders.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.54,0:09:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,當他被指示將基金貸款 貸給菲立浦葛林…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}When he was told to give a pension-fund loan to Philip Green...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.75,0:10:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,六千兩百七十萬的支票…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}...this check for $62,700,000...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.92,0:10:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,給全新的坦吉樂\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}for the new Tangiers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.88,0:10:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他就會乖乖聽話\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}...he did what he was told.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.84,0:10:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他可是最完美的傀儡\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: Here was the perfect front man.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.72,0:10:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他還能幹嘛呢？ 他什麼都不知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}What the fuck else could he be? He didn't know too much.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.35,0:10:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,也什麼都不想知道…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He didn't want to know too much...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.98,0:10:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是老大們讓工會借錢給他\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}especially that the bosses made the Teamsters lend him money.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.85,0:10:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,他想相信他們是因為 他的才智貸款給他\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He wanted to believe they gave him the money because he was smart.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.32,0:10:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我瞭解這城市的競爭性有多大 才會說出此話\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I say that knowing just how much competition we have in this city.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.20,0:10:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他們從哪兒找來葛林的？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: And where they got Green from?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.41,0:10:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,誰知道啊？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Who the fuck knows?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我只知道他在亞利桑那州 是個房地產經紀…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}All I know is that he was an Arizona real-estate hustler...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.87,0:10:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,卻連開來拿支票的油錢 都差點付不出來\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}who barely had enough gas money to come and pick up his fucking check.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.21,0:10:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,美國中部 卡車司機工會退休基金 是由老大的人…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}And it was the bosses' man...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.17,0:10:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,安迪史東下所有的命令\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Andy Stone, who gave all the orders.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.09,0:10:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,並不是由董事會主席 菲立浦葛林\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Not the Chairman of the Board, Philip Green.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.59,0:10:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我瞭解\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I understand.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.77,0:10:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,現在只缺…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: Now all they needed was...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.06,0:10:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,一個可信任的人來管理賭場\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}someone they could trust to run the casino.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.36,0:10:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,有誰比艾斯更適合？ 他已經在賭城混了幾年…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}And who better than Ace? He was already in Vegas a couple years...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他對這兒瞭若指掌\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}and he had the fucking place clocked.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.61,0:11:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,艾斯的一貫作風 你給他個管理賭場的機會…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}But typical Ace, give him a shot to run a casino...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.37,0:11:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他還推三阻四\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}and he tries to talk you out of it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.99,0:11:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道自己行不行\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I don't know if I could do this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.74,0:11:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,賭博遊樂委員會絕不會 發執照給我的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}The Gaming Commission would never give me a license.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.16,0:11:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我最起碼有兩打以上 賭博與賽馬被逮的前科\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I have at least 24 gambling and bookmaking pinches on me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.38,0:11:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,在賭場工作不需要執照\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You don't have to have a license to work in a casino.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.71,0:11:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你只需要去申請\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}All you gotta do is apply for one.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.67,0:11:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,州法律允許你在申請期間…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}The State law says that you can work in a casino...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.30,0:11:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,在賭場做事\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}while they process your application.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他們檔進度現在落後十年\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}ANDY: They got a 10-year backlog.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.01,0:11:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,若他們發現了怎麼辦？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}What happens when they do find out?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.73,0:11:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他們為什麼會想發現？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}ANDY: Why would they want to find out?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.56,0:11:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我們在這兒投資了一億\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}We're putting $100 million here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.50,0:11:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他們何必趕我們走？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Why would they lock us out?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.40,0:11:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,他們不會發現的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}ANDY: They'll never find out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.94,0:11:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你只需要一直改變職位頭銜\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}All you gotta do is keep changing your job title.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.40,0:11:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,像從賭場執行長改到 餐飲主席\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Like, from Casino Executive to Food and Beverage Chairman.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.99,0:11:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,然後他們又會將你的申請表 擺到最下麵去\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Then they put your application at the bottom of the pile.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.16,0:11:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我有大把的員工 已經工作三十年了還沒執照\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I know guys who've worked there for 30 years don't have a license.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.25,0:11:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是容易的決定，安迪\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}It's a tough proposition, Andy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.59,0:11:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,若我去做，得讓我用我的方式\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}If I did it, I'd have to run it my way.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.76,0:11:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}ANDY: You got it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.92,0:11:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我說真的，不能有干涉\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I'm serious. No interference.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.30,0:11:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有人會干涉你管理賭場\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Nobody's gonna interfere with your running the casino.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.60,0:11:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我保證\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I guarantee it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.94,0:12:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,艾斯就是這樣接手的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: And that's how they got Ace to take over.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.94,0:12:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,要艾斯是因為 他不管是吃喝拉撒睡時都在賭\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}They wanted him because Ace ate, slept and breathed gambling.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.11,0:12:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,他們還給了他個很可愛的頭銜…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}They worked out a real cute job title, too...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.62,0:12:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,坦吉樂公關理事\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Tangiers Public Relations Director.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.12,0:12:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,但他只管賭場\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}But the only thing he ever directed was the casino.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.87,0:12:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他從十五歲時第一次下注就沒輸過\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He made his first bet when he was 15, and he always made money.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.55,0:12:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他不像你我那樣賭\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He didn't bet like you or me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.59,0:12:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,就為了他媽的好玩\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Having some fun with it, shit like that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.72,0:12:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪兒學當莊家的？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Where did you learn how to deal?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.10,0:12:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他下注時就像是腦部外科醫生一樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: He bet like a fucking brain surgeon.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,籌碼得擺對\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Place the checks properly.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,-像這樣 -是的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-That's the way you do it. -Yes, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.31,0:12:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,他得洞悉一切\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: He had to know everything.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.15,0:12:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他知道沒人曉得的內幕…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He'd find out the inside stuff nobody else knew...{\r}
