Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.88,0:18:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他有關係的 他是縣輔導的表兄弟\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He's juiced in. He's the County Commissioner's cousin.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.71,0:18:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我連清潔工都不會給他做\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: I wouldn't give the bum a mop job.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.67,0:18:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,別無選擇，我必須照顧他們\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I had no choice. I had to take care of them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.43,0:18:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,這些鄉巴佬當權\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}These yokels ran the state.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.22,0:18:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,多謝，議員\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}DEALER: Thanks, Senator.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.47,0:18:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-他們立法，又掌管法院 -我要開房間\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: They passed the laws, owned the courts. I need a room.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.64,0:18:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我每週都有十多個政客來訪\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: I had dozens of politicians and state officials coming through weekly.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.73,0:18:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,-他要什麼都給他 -當然\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Get him what he wants. BILLY: Certainly.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.73,0:18:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,何不讓他們快樂？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Why not make them happy?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.29,0:18:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,對於政客 例如我們這位州議員…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}For politicians, like our State Senator up there...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.42,0:18:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都是免費的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}everything was on the house.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.96,0:19:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他們的招待生涯 在當選時就贏得了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}These guys won their comped life when they got elected.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.09,0:19:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,何不加以利用？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Why not take advantage of it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.76,0:19:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,政客還是小事，我們解決的了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Still, the politicians came cheap. We could handle them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.93,0:19:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是像市川那種…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}It's a whale, like K.K. Ichikawa...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.60,0:19:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,百家樂一把下三萬的豪賭客\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}who plays $30, 000 a hand in baccarat.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.94,0:19:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,這種才該看緊\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}That's the one you really gotta watch.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.98,0:19:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他下注動作快，玩得大 他的資金雄厚…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He plays fast and big. He has the cash and the credit...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.57,0:19:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,足可把你玩垮\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}to turn out your lights.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.07,0:19:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,一年前他讓開曼群島上 好幾家賭場洗底\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}A year ago he cleaned out a couple of casinos in the Cayman Islands.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.16,0:19:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他從賭場贏了我們兩百萬…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Downstairs he takes us for $2 million...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.54,0:19:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,又從酒店套房拿了免費的 肥皂、洗髮精與毛巾\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}and upstairs he takes free soap, shampoo and towels.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.63,0:19:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,又是一個 喜愛免費套房…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Another billionaire cheapskate who loved his free rooms...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.05,0:19:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,免費私人飛機又賺得我們兩百萬 的億萬富翁小氣鬼\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}free private jets and $2 million of our money.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.84,0:19:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我們也不好惹\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}But we got him back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.14,0:19:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我讓機師告訴他飛機故障\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I had our pilot tell him the plane was on the fritz.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.81,0:19:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-發生什麼事？ -非常抱歉\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}ICHlKAWA: What went wrong? BILLY: I'm awfully sorry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.98,0:19:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是機械故障\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}These mechanical things happen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.98,0:19:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,在這兒總比在上面好\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Better here than up there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.65,0:19:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,然後他趕不上回日本的飛機\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Then he missed the flights connecting with Japan.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.32,0:19:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然沒有空房\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I can't believe there's no room.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.58,0:20:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我們給了他一整樓的房間\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: We got him back with a whole floor of rooms to himself.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.08,0:20:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-真抱歉讓你趕不上飛機\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-Sorry you missed your plane.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.56,0:20:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-你想要贏回我的錢啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-You'd like some of my money back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.17,0:20:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不，不賭了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, no. No gambling.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.88,0:20:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他回來後開始下小注\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: And once he was back, he played small.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.51,0:20:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,一把只賭一千 而不是平常的三萬一把\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He bet $1,000 a hand, instead of his usual $30,000 a hand.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.56,0:20:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,但我知道這些豪賭客的習性…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}But I knew the trick with whales like Ichikawa...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.57,0:20:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他們不可能一直下小注的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}was that they can't bet small for long.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.11,0:20:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他不覺得是贏一萬…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He didn't think of it as winning $10, 000...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.57,0:20:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他會想成是輸九萬…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}he thought of it as losing $90, 000.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.87,0:20:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他開始加碼\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}So, he upped his bets.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.88,0:20:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,直到他將贏得的輸光 再加上自己一百萬的現金\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Until he dropped his winnings back and gave up $1 million of his own cash.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.88,0:20:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,在賭場堙A第一原則就是 讓他們一直賭…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}In a casino, the cardinal rule is to keep them playing...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.89,0:20:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,也讓他們一直回來\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}and keep them coming back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.39,0:20:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,賭得越多就輸得越多\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}The longer they play, the more they lose.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.06,0:21:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,最終錢就都是我們的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}In the end, we get it all.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.57,0:21:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,在賭城，每個人都得注意著別人\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}In Vegas, everybody's gotta watch everybody else.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.87,0:21:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,玩家是來贏賭場錢的…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Since the players are looking to beat the casino...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.92,0:21:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,莊家得看好玩家…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}the dealers are watching the players...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.26,0:21:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,收付賭注得看好莊家…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}the boxmen are watching the dealers...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.13,0:21:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,管場的注意著收付賭注的人…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}the floormen are watching the boxmen...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.10,0:21:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,賭區經理看著管場的…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}the pit bosses are watching the floormen...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.93,0:21:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,值班經理看著賭區經理…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}the shift bosses are watching the pit bosses...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.85,0:21:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,賭場經理看著值班經理…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}the casino manager is watching the shift bosses...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.77,0:21:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我則看著賭場經理…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I'm watching the casino manager...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.11,0:21:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,而監視照相機看著我們大家\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}and the eye in the sky is watching us all.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.70,0:21:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,另外，還有十多個傢伙…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Plus, we had a dozen guys...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.87,0:21:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,大多以前都是老千 他們知道所有的騙術\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}most of them ex-cheats, who knew every trick in the house.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.02,0:22:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊！\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Yes!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.77,0:22:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,-非常好 -我就跟你說我今天很旺\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-Very nice. -I told you I was hot tonight.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.17,0:22:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好樣的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Looking good.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.21,0:22:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧，為了金吉兒，快\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}MAN: Let's go. This is for Ginger.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.21,0:22:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,一百賭你沒老A\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}MAN: Let me have $100 on your hard 10.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.26,0:22:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.39,0:22:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}MAN: Here we go now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.86,0:22:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-對不起 -骰子\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-Oh, I'm sorry. -The dice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.90,0:22:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,多謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Thank you very much.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.58,0:23:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,多謝你\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I appreciate that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.74,0:23:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,保重，史蒂夫 要冒險啊，開快車\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Take care, Steve. Take chances, drive fast.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.46,0:23:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,這一百給你，甜心 多謝你賞光\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}This $100 is for you, love. Thanks for your time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.55,0:23:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-快點 -怎麼了？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-Come on. -What's the matter?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.38,0:23:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我幫你賺了不少，我要我的份\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I made a lot of money for you, I want my cut.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.22,0:23:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼錢？我看到你偷錢\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}What money? I've seen you stealing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.14,0:23:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,“什麼錢？” 你看看這堆籌碼\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}"What money?" Look at the stack of chips.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.64,0:23:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,-我要我的一半 -我觀察你一夜了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}GINGER: I want my half. GAMBLER: I've watched you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.93,0:23:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,-我要我的錢 -你皮包堨是熟籌碼\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-I want my money. -Your bag is full of chips.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.44,0:23:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,-我才沒偷你的東西 -滾吧！\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}GINGER: I didn't steal anything from you. GAMBLER: Get lost!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.82,0:23:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,-滾吧？ -沒錯！\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}GINGER: Get lost? GAMBLER: Yes!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.74,0:23:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-這怎麼樣呢？ -別這樣！\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-Well, how about that? -Come on!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.21,0:24:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,真酷，讓我一見鍾情\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: What a move. I fell in love right there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.47,0:24:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但在賭城，像金吉兒這樣的女孩 得花上大錢\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}But in Vegas, for a girl like Ginger, love costs money.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.81,0:24:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我去補個妝\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I'm gonna go powder my nose.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.74,0:24:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-金吉兒的人生目標是錢 -馬上回來\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Ginger's mission in life was money. I'll be right back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.04,0:24:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-待會見，金吉兒 -多謝你\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}DOORMAN: See you. GINGER: Thanks for asking.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.17,0:24:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,她在賭場可是皇后\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: She was a queen around the casino.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.00,0:25:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,她召來大賭客 並也幫他們花大錢\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}She brought in high rollers and helped them spend a lot of money.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.80,0:25:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-你好 -嘿，金吉兒，你好嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-Hello. -Hey, Ginger. How you doing?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.09,0:25:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好得很，一點小意思 你幫我搞定了嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}GINGER: Great. You might have something for me. Got me covered?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.85,0:25:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-非常感謝 -自己保重喔\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}GINGER: Thank you. VALET: Take care of yourself.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.22,0:25:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我有些幸運丸給你，安迪\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I got some lucky pills for you, Andy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.94,0:25:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,誰不想要金吉兒？ 她是城埵W聲最響亮…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Who didn't want her? She was one of the best known...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.77,0:25:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,也是道上最受歡迎的江湖人物\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}best liked and most respected hustlers in town.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.78,0:25:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,像她這麼聰明的玩家 可以讓男人…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Smart hustlers like her could keep a guy awake...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.24,0:25:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,兩三天不睡 然後再讓他一文不名的…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}for two or three days before sending him home broke...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.79,0:25:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,回到老婆與銀行審查主任身邊\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}to the little woman and his bank examiners.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.22,0:25:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,有找錢嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Any change?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.77,0:25:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來時小賭了幾把\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, I hit a few games on the way back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.61,0:25:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那根本是胡扯 她把錢收起來了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: But that was all bullshit. She just pocketed the cash.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.57,0:25:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-你今天好嗎？ -不錯啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}GINGER: How you doing tonight? CASHlER: Good.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.57,0:26:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-你呢？ -衰死了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}CASHlER: How are you? GINGER: Beat.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.24,0:26:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,-金吉兒洞悉玩家們的習性 -給你一百\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Ginger had the hustlers' code. GINGER: Take one for you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.96,0:26:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-多謝 -她懂得如何買通他人\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}CASHlER: Thank you. SAM: She knew how to take care of people.{\r}
