Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.01,0:27:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我所認識的金吉兒 根本不會多看這怪胎一眼\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: The Ginger I knew wouldn't even look at this creep.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.01,0:27:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,-祝你好運 -是啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-Good luck. -Yeah.{\r}
