Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.72,0:28:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,就連去渡個假 他們在機場時都不放過他\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Even after a vacation, they hassled him at the airport.{\r}
