Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.82,0:28:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,他們隨時願意嫁禍於他 不管是在哪兒發生什麼事\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: They were ready to blame him for anything, no matter where.{\r}
