Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.74,0:28:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,因為尼奇很喜歡混幫派\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Because Nicky enjoyed being a gangster.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.70,0:28:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他也不在乎有誰知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}And he didn't give a damn who knew it.{\r}
