Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.22,0:28:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,別急於辯護 可能還有些卡在你頭髮傜N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Don't get so defensive, it could be stuck in your hair.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.27,0:28:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}What's that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.61,0:28:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有了，謝謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}There's no more. Thanks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.78,0:28:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我迫不及待想去拉斯維加斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: I couldn't wait to get my hands on Vegas.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.82,0:29:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,但老大可不是送我去玩的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}But the bosses didn't send me out to have a good time.{\r}
