Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.13,0:29:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，山姆\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, Sammy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.80,0:29:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-天呀，瞧瞧這地方 -不可思議\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-Boy, look at this place. -Incredible.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.30,0:29:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎來賭城\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Welcome to Vegas.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.85,0:29:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-好樣的，山姆 -不錯吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: Okay, Sammy. SAM: Something, huh?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.81,0:29:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,金吉兒\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Ginger.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.65,0:29:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,靠，你都在這兒幹嘛？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Holy shit. What've you been doing out here?{\r}
