Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.99,0:29:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,這是珍妮佛與尼克 我的好朋友們\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}This is Jennifer and Nick. They're dear friends of mine.{\r}
