Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.50,0:29:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,晚餐後，我們讓珍妮佛 與金吉兒一塊兒…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: After we ate, we left Jennifer and Ginger...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.21,0:29:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我們倆則出去談話\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}and we took a ride to talk.{\r}
