Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.59,0:29:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得我也搬來如何？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}What do you think about me moving out here?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.51,0:29:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,有問題嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You got a problem with that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.22,0:29:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,當然沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}No, of course not.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.56,0:30:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你是說你允許羅？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You mean I have your permission?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.52,0:30:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,當然羅 但我得告訴你…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Sure, you do. But I just gotta tell you...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.69,0:30:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,在這兒可不能開玩笑\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}it's no joke out here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.73,0:30:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你得保持低調\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You gotta keep a low profile.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.90,0:30:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不像是在老家 這兒他們不喜歡我們\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}It's not like back home. They don't like guys like us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.91,0:30:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,警長是個不折不扣的牛仔\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}This sheriff's a real cowboy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.03,0:30:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,連巡警都不怕在沙漠堮I人\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Even coppers aren't afraid to bury people in the desert.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.74,0:30:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我不在乎 我只想離開老家一陣子\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I don't care. I want to get away from back home for a while.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.92,0:30:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我厭倦了那傜N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I'm tired of that shit back there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.92,0:30:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,看看這地方，簡直是錢砌的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Look at this place. It's made of money.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.84,0:30:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,知道最屌的是什麼？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You know what the best part is?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.38,0:30:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,沒人知道我們在幹嘛\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Nobody's gonna know what we're doing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.38,0:30:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,沒人看著我們，大家都在老家\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}There's nobody here to see us. Everybody's back home.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.55,0:30:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我無緣故被逮了兩次\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I got pinched twice for no reason.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.47,0:30:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我真得小心了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I really gotta be careful.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.27,0:30:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我管理的地方是有執照的 全是合法的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I'm running a licensed place. Everything's legit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.89,0:30:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,別擔心，我什麼都不會做的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Don't worry about it. I'm not gonna do anything.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.60,0:30:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我尤其不會拖你下水\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I'm especially not gonna involve you in anything.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.78,0:30:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,艾斯看賭城的觀點…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: Ace saw Vegas one way...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.57,0:30:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,-你跟他說過我要來嗎？ -當然\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: Call and tell him I'm coming? JACK: Of course.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.91,0:30:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我的看法不同\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}...but I saw it another.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.58,0:30:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我視它為未開發的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I saw it as untouched.{\r}
