Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.65,0:31:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,他們能怎樣？逼迫尼奇？ 尼奇就是逼迫者\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}What were they gonna do? Muscle Nicky? Nicky was the muscle.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.95,0:31:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,-你好嗎？ -你好嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-Hey, how you doing? -How you doing?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.78,0:31:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,-你有東西給我嗎？ -什麼東西？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-You got that thing for me? -What thing?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.95,0:31:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,尼奇，我以為你是來下注的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Nicky, I thought you was laying.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.12,0:31:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,下注？不，我來收錢\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I was laying? No, I'm taking it.{\r}
