Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.17,0:31:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,或許在我把你的臉砸過這窗戶後…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Maybe if I stick your fucking face through this window...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.01,0:31:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你就會清楚點\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}you'll get unconfused.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.68,0:31:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-把錢他媽的給我 -對不起\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-Give me the fucking money. -I'm sorry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.60,0:31:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是故意的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I didn't mean anything by it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.01,0:31:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你連錢都準備好了 你他媽的以為我要下注\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}That's why you had it ready. You thought I was laying it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.81,0:31:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-我的頭 -放聰明點\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-My fucking head. -Smarten up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.48,0:31:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,而現在尼可拉斯山多羅 要來跟我們說第一總統的故事了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}And now Nicholas Santoro will come up and tell us about our first President.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.49,0:32:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,喬治華盛頓出生在…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}George Washington was born--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.99,0:32:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,但最起碼還風平浪靜了一陣子\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: But still, it was nice and quiet for a while.{\r}
