Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.84,0:32:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,結果其中的一位教練 是市立警察局情報單位的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Turned out that one of the other coaches was a metro intelligence cop.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.35,0:32:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不過無所謂，這純粹是孩子的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}But it didn't matter. It was all about the kids.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.02,0:32:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他得明白不是每棒都能揮出全壘打\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He's gotta realize everything can't be a home run.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.56,0:32:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是這樣告訴他 不過那小子就是這樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}That's exactly what I tell him, but that's the kind of kid he is.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.19,0:32:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,尼奇就是尼奇 他總是引人注目\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: And Nicky being Nicky, he made his presence known.{\r}
