Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.50,0:32:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,像在那邊的那兩個蠢才\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Like these two fucking balloon heads over here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.00,0:32:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,想從我們這兒騙走二十萬\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}They were gonna try to bang us out of $200, 000.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.92,0:32:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,走著瞧\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, right, I'm sure.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.76,0:32:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你好嗎？你怎麼會在這兒？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}How are you? What are you doing here?{\r}
