Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.91,0:33:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他不在這兒？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He's not here?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.96,0:33:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他出去了？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Carmine's out?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.04,0:33:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他好像過了馬路還是什麼的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I think he went across the street or somewhere else or something.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.51,0:33:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是喔，聽著，祝你在這兒好運\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Well, listen, good luck with the joint.{\r}
