Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.77,0:33:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,也祝你好運\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Good luck to you, too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.35,0:33:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他們忘了簽名\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}CASHlER: They forgot to sign their papers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.36,0:33:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,他們不需要這個了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}They don't need those anymore.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.03,0:33:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,因為基本尊重 我只給別幫傢伙一點警告\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Out of respect, guys from other crews got away with a warning.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.45,0:33:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,其他的人可得小心了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Everybody else, watch out.{\r}
