Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.42,0:33:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,被我們抓到後又會溜回來…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}We'd catch them and they'd try to sneak back...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.63,0:33:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,戴著假鬍子、假髮、假鼻子\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}with beards and wigs and fake noses.{\r}
