Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.60,0:34:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,每次下五百，不過只有個小問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}at $500 each with only one little problem.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.97,0:34:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他每次都猜對\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He's always guessed right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.56,0:34:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,要不是他這麼貪心 可能還不會這麼明顯\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}If he wasn't so fucking greedy, he'd have been tougher to spot.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.44,0:34:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不過到頭來，他們每個都貪\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}But in the end, they're all greedy.{\r}
