Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.57,0:37:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,在大庭廣眾數這麼多錢\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}That's a lot of money to be counting out in public.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.53,0:38:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,為何不讓我拿到辦公室確認？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Why don't I take him over to the office and verify it?{\r}
