Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.00,0:38:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,順便叫一瓶好香檳來\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}By the way, send over a nice bottle of champagne on ice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.67,0:38:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,-沒問題 -要很特別的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}CASHlER: Sure will. BILLY: Real special.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.50,0:38:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,對了，我是賭場經理 比利雪伯堤\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}By the way, I'm Billy Sherbert, casino manager.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.71,0:38:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-還玩得愉快嗎？ -是的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}BILLY: Having a good time? HUSTLER 2: Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.55,0:38:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你在較有隱私的地方算比較好\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You want to count the money in privacy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.89,0:38:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我得趕飛機去克堣痁騱N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}HUSTLER 2: I have a plane to catch.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.30,0:38:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以領取我贏得的錢嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Can I get my winnings?{\r}
