Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.11,0:38:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我給你一個選擇\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: I'm gonna give you a choice:{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.78,0:38:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以拿錢然後被錘頭砸 或者是從這兒走出去\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You can have the money and the hammer, or you can walk out of here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.49,0:38:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,-你要哪個？ -我要走\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-What do you want? -I wanna get out of here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.74,0:38:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,告訴你那群朋友，他們若來亂搞 會發生什麼事\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Tell your friends what happens if they fuck around here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.25,0:38:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,-對不起，我犯了大錯 -你真他媽的說對了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-I'm sorry, I made a bad mistake. -You're fucking right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.92,0:38:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你們要是再敢回來 我會敲爛你們的頭\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: If you come back, either one of you, we'll break your fucking heads.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.59,0:38:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到那鋸子沒？不是放著好看的 不要再出現在這傜N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You see that fucking saw? We're gonna use it. You don't fuck around here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.22,0:38:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-懂嗎？ -是\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Got it? HUSTLER 2: Yes.{\r}
