Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.30,0:38:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,把他丟到後街去 跟條子說他被車撞到了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Throw him out in the alley. Tell the cops he got hit by a car.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.18,0:38:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不到一會兒，一切就都搞定了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Within no time, everything was set in place.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.30,0:39:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我們弄走了那些老千 盈利上揚好多…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}We got rid of the freelance scamsters, the pro was way up...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.68,0:39:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,上頭老大高興極了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}the gods were happy, or as happy as the gods can ever be.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.94,0:39:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,然後我決定將生活複雜化\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}And I decided to complicate my life.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.35,0:39:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,對不愛冒險的我來說…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}For a guy who likes sure things...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.11,0:39:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我用我的下半輩子 下了筆勝算不大的賭注\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I was about to bet the rest of my life on a real long shot.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.99,0:39:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我們也不年輕了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}We're not getting any younger.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.86,0:39:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你不覺得是時候了？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Don't you think it's time?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.86,0:39:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你對這些不厭煩嗎？ 這邊睡、那邊混？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Aren't you getting tired of all this shit? Banging around, hustling around?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.54,0:39:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-你想要妨礙我嗎？ -我想給你更好的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-Are you trying to handicap me? -I'm gonna do you one better.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.75,0:39:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我想娶你進門\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I'm trying to marry you.{\r}
