Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.55,0:39:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我說真的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: I'm serious.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.55,0:39:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我想定下來，想有個家\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I wanna settle down. I want a family.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.85,0:39:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你找錯人了，山姆\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You got the wrong girl, Sam.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.85,0:39:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我會是個好爸爸 你也將是個好媽媽\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I'd be a good father, you'd be a good mother.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.19,0:39:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道我\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You don't know me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.65,0:39:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你才認識我兩、三個月 你瞭解什麼？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You've known me two, three months. What do you know?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.48,0:39:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經43歲了，我不想再等了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I'm 43 years old. I don't want to wait.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.24,0:39:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我對你的瞭解深到 令我自己知道我非常愛你\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I know you well enough to know that I really love you very much.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.49,0:39:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我心目中最理想的人\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I can't think of anybody better to be with.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.33,0:39:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想再等了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I don't feel like waiting anymore.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.00,0:40:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你見過很多婚姻美滿的人嗎？ 我可沒見過\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You know a lot of happily married people? 'Cause I don't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.34,0:40:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,這我都懂\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I know all that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.59,0:40:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我在乎你\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I care about you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.06,0:40:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,但我對你沒有那種感覺\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}But I just don't have those kind of feelings for you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.40,0:40:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起，我並不愛你\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I'm sorry. I'm not in love with you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.61,0:40:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-好的 -懂嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: All right. GINGER: Understand?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.74,0:40:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}GINGER: I'm sorry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.91,0:40:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}No....{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.62,0:40:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那可以培養\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}That can grow.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.13,0:40:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,只要互相尊重 感情是可以培養的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}As long as there's a mutual respect, that kind of thing can grow.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.84,0:40:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我很現實，我可以接受\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I'm realistic. I can accept that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.76,0:40:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,愛到底是什麼？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: What is love anyway?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.55,0:40:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不就是互相尊重 不就是一心一意\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: It's a mutual respect. It's a devotion.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.31,0:40:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是一個人在乎另一個人\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}It's a caring from one person to another.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.10,0:40:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,若我們可以設立一個基礎…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}And if we could set up some kind of foundation...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.15,0:40:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,以相互尊重為底…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}based on that mutual respect...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.28,0:41:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得遲早你會對我有情…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I feel that eventually you would care enough about me...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.41,0:41:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣我能接受\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}that I could live with that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.45,0:41:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,若行不通的話…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}If it doesn't work out...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.33,0:41:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,若行不通的話 那我怎麼辦？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}if it doesn't play out, then what happens to me?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.33,0:41:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在做得不錯 往後會越來越好\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I'm doing well now. I'm gonna do even better.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.50,0:41:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不論如何…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}So whatever happens...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.67,0:41:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,就算我們倆行不通…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}if it doesn't work out between us...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.67,0:41:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我都會確保你下半輩子的生活\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I'll make sure you're okay for the rest of your life.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.51,0:41:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其如果有了孩子…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}If there are kids, especially...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.18,0:41:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我會給你今生最好的照料\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I'll take care of you better than you'd imagine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.39,0:41:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-你葫蘆到底賣什麼藥？ -我都明講了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}GINGER: What are you pitching me? SAM: Just what I said.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.06,0:41:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你下半輩子都不用愁\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You'll be set up for the rest of your life.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.98,0:41:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,這我可保證\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}That I can promise you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.07,0:41:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要試試？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Want to take a chance?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.46,0:41:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我娶金吉兒時就聽過她的一切往事…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: When I married Ginger, I knew all the stories...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.46,0:41:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不在乎 我是山姆羅斯坦\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}but I didn't give a fuck. I'm Sam Rothstein, I said.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.26,0:41:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我能改變她\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I can change her.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.97,0:42:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,這是典型的艾斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: It was typical Ace.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.56,0:42:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他請了城堜狾釭漱j人物 他知道他們都會出席\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He invited the biggest people in town. He knew they'd show.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.94,0:42:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他知道他們都有求於他\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He knew they all wanted something from him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.44,0:42:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,艾斯絕對不可能不求回報 連金吉兒也不例外\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}With Ace, nobody ever got a free ride. Even Ginger.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.78,0:42:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,一切還是依他行事\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}With her, he still covered his bets.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.74,0:42:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他們在結婚前得先有孩子\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}They had to have the baby first, before they could get married.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.87,0:42:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他甚至還托我們幫忙看艾美幾天…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He even made us watch Amy for a few days...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.49,0:42:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好讓他們去渡蜜月\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}when they went on their honeymoon.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.04,0:42:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,無所謂啊 我們愛死那孩子\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I didn't mind, we loved the kid.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.38,0:42:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你感到我的眼神？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}LESTER: Can you feel my eyes on you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.59,0:42:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你感到我看透你的心嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Can you feel me look into your heart?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.93,0:42:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你能感到我躺在你肚皮上嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Can you feel me in the pit of your stomach?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.64,0:42:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你能在體內感受我？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Can you feel me in you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.19,0:42:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,在心堙H\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}In your heart?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.23,0:42:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,別等我過去\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Don't make me come there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.95,0:42:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,回答我\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Answer me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.86,0:42:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我愛你\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}GINGER: [Crying] I love you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.45,0:42:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,寶貝，你知道我也愛你嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Baby, do you know that I love you, too?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.74,0:42:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,-不，萊斯特 -你知道嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}GINGER: No, Lester. LESTER: Do you know that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.83,0:42:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}GINGER: Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.29,0:43:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我目前能為自己做的 最好的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}This is the best thing I can do for my life right now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.46,0:43:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}That's right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.80,0:43:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,所以會沒事的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}So it's going to be okay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.67,0:43:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你發誓？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Promise?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.55,0:43:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你幸福\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I wish you all the luck in the world.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.64,0:43:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-真的？ -是，我真的這麼想\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}GINGER: You do? LESTER: Yeah, I do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.22,0:43:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,這是你目前能做的最好的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}It's the best thing you can do right now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.69,0:43:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我說真的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I mean this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.31,0:43:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你生活會很安穩\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You have real security.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.52,0:43:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,甜心，你將坐在賭城最有利的位子\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Sweetheart, you're gonna be situated just right in Vegas.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.32,0:43:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,這對我們來說再好不過了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Come on. This is great for us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.11,0:43:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我會一直都在你身邊的 我哪兒都不會去\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I'm always gonna be here for you. I ain't going no place.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.04,0:43:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在就在看著你\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I'm looking at you right now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.83,0:43:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,仿佛生平第一次見到你似的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I'm seeing you for the very first time, right this minute.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.25,0:43:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我可聽到我的心悸動\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I'm saying I can feel my heart click.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.30,0:43:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到你十四歲時\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I see you 14 years old.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.97,0:43:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我在見你的第一秒就看到你了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I see you the first second I ever saw you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.43,0:43:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到你，像匹長腿的小馬兒…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I see you, long-legged little colt...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.97,0:43:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,還戴著蠢蠢的牙套\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}stupid braces on your teeth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.27,0:43:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-好吧 -我每次見你時都看到這些\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, then. LESTER: Every time I see you, that's what I see.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.35,0:43:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,再聊羅，再見\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Talk to you later. Bye.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.66,0:44:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-你還好嗎？ -嗯\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-You all right? -Yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.79,0:44:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼哭？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Why are you crying?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.58,0:44:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒有哭\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I'm not crying.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.42,0:44:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-別喝這麼多了吧 -我沒事\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-Maybe you shouldn't drink so much. -I'm okay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.39,0:44:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你能理解\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You just have to understand.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.85,0:44:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我自小就跟萊斯特在一起\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I've been with Lester since I was a kid.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.03,0:44:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想道別\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I just wanted to say goodbye.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.24,0:44:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I just....{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.95,0:44:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我有權這樣做\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I think I have a right to do that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.37,0:44:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}GINGER: Okay?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.62,0:44:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}It's all right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.50,0:44:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你那段人生已經完結了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}That part of your life is over with.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.17,0:44:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-不是嗎？ -是的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Right? GINGER: Yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.22,0:44:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你現在跟我\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You're with me now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.05,0:45:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,-是的 -不是嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-Yeah. -Right?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.89,0:45:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-你確定嗎？ -是的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: You're sure? GINGER: Yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.53,0:45:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-要走了嗎？我們回去吧 -好的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Want to go? Let's go back in. GINGER: Okay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.71,0:45:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}GINGER: It's great.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.18,0:45:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,都是我的東西，天呀\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}GINGER: It's all my stuff. Oh, my God.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.14,0:45:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你把我的東西都帶來了！\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You brought all my stuff!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.47,0:45:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I can't....{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.39,0:46:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,試試看，這是你的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Try it on. It's yours.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.85,0:46:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,別開玩笑了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You're kidding.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.32,0:46:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}My God.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.40,0:46:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-是什麼毛？ -是龍貓\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-What is it? -It's chinchilla.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.53,0:46:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好軟喔\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}It's so soft.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.32,0:46:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,很好喔？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Nice, isn't it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.70,0:46:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,從沒有人對我這麼好\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}No one's ever been so nice to me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.63,0:46:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我的老天！\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}GINGER: Oh, my God!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.14,0:46:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我要是在同一天將它們全都戴上 會不會太過火啊？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Do you think it's too much if I wear these all on the same day?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.52,0:46:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你想怎樣就怎樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You can do whatever you want.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.85,0:46:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我有沒有實現我的諾言啊？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Do I keep my promises or do I keep my promises?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.56,0:46:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你太好了 這些珠寶也不錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You're so wonderful. The jewelry's not so bad either.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.57,0:46:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我們不應該把這些放在家 應該擺到銀行去\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}We shouldn't keep this in the house. We gotta put it in the bank.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.44,0:46:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能留一副在家嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Come on. Can I keep this one in the house?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.45,0:46:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,仔細聽好\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Pay attention to me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.32,0:47:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我要告訴你一件重要的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}What I'm gonna tell you is very important.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.45,0:47:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,這全部都不算什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}All this stuff doesn't mean anything.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.62,0:47:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,錢財珠寶 如果沒有信任就毫無意義\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Money, this, doesn't mean anything without trust.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.29,0:47:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我得要信任你到可將生命交給你\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I have to be able to trust you with my life.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.17,0:47:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,洛杉磯
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.30,0:47:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,總價值超過一百萬的現金與珠寶 鎖在賭城的銀行堙K\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: With over $1 million in cash and jewels tucked in a bank in Vegas...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.10,0:47:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,全歸她所有 金吉兒非常有安全感\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}only for Ginger, she was secure and happy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.43,0:47:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,她最愛那些\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}She loved that shit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.31,0:47:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,但在我這行 手上得有許多流動的現金\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}But a guy in my line of work has to have a lot of payoff cash around.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.57,0:47:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,貪污的條子與綁匪 他們都不收支票\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Crooked cops and kidnappers, they don't take checks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.73,0:47:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,考林先生，需要幫忙嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Need any help with that, Mr. Collins?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.86,0:47:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我在洛杉磯的銀行 也擺了兩百萬…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: So I put $2 million cash in a Los Angeles bank...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.49,0:47:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,用考林先生與夫人的名義\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}under the name of Mr. and Mrs. Tom Collins.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.74,0:47:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,這純粹是我個人的贖金與保金\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}This was strictly my shakedown and kidnapping money.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.12,0:47:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,因為在我最需要這筆錢時 我不是蹲在牢奡N是被關在衣櫃…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Since I'd be in jail or locked in a closet when I needed the money most...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.67,0:47:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我將這筆錢唯一的鑰匙 給了金吉兒好讓我能保命\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I gave Ginger the only key to the cash that could get me back alive.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.94,0:48:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,這是簽名卡\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}This is just a signature card.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.48,0:48:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,她簽了之後就會是世上…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Once she signs, she'll be the only person...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.94,0:48:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,唯一可以開保險箱的人 連我都開啟不了？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}to have total access to the box, no one else, including myself?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.49,0:48:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，這是你的要求\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}BANKER: That's right. That's the way you wanted it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.99,0:48:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,山姆，我問你個問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Sam, let me ask you a question.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.79,0:48:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定很信任你老婆\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You must really trust your wife.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.54,0:48:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，怎麼啦？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Sure I do. Why?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.13,0:48:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,很好啊，只是很少見\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}It's good. It's just unusual.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.88,0:48:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,實不相瞞 我有很多客戶都不信任\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}To tell you the truth, so many of my clients don't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.02,0:48:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,將金吉兒還有錢的事解決後 我安心多了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: With Ginger and the money in place, I felt covered.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.90,0:49:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,為了安全起見，我又將頭銜…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}To play it safe, I switched job titles again...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.49,0:49:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,換成餐飲董事\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}and made myself Food and Beverage Director.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.82,0:49:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣一來就沒人可以 為執照的事找我麻煩\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}This way nobody would bother me about a license.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.49,0:49:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,賭城對我來說像是個夢\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Vegas was like a dream for me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.58,0:49:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,問題是尼奇也夢想著 他自己的賭城\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Trouble was Nicky was dreaming of his own kind of Vegas.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.50,0:49:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我將錢放出，每天三分利\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: I put money out on the street charging three points a week.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.87,0:49:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,莊家高利貸\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Juice to the dealers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.13,0:49:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,-別逼我們找上門 -你不會需要這樣的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-Don't make us look for you. -You won't have to look for me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.59,0:49:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,多謝了，尼奇\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I appreciate it. Thanks, Nicky.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.59,0:49:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他們不是爛賭鬼就是爛毒鬼\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: They were degenerate gamblers, coke freaks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.26,0:49:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,沒多久，坦吉樂一半的莊家 都在我手掌心傜N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}In no time, I had half the dealers in the Tangiers in my pocket.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.35,0:49:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,下一步，我開始出千騙大賭客的錢\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Then, the next thing I did, I started busting out high-stakes poker players.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.02,0:49:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好明顯\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: It was so obvious.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.60,0:49:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,尼奇所有的小把戲 全都是靠手勢\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}All of Nicky's half-assed mechanics, they were signal-happy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.86,0:49:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我下五百\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I'm gonna open for $500.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.65,0:49:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,互相打手勢\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Signaling back and forth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.45,0:49:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,尼奇以為沒人注意到他 但是他錯了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Nicky thought nobody was watching him. But he was wrong.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.37,0:49:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想要那些探員在我的地盤\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I didn't want any of those agents near my place.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.03,0:49:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,-四條A -我不相信\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-Four aces. -I can't believe this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.83,0:49:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我唯一的運氣好像就是手氣背\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}GAMBLER 2: If I didn't have bad luck, I wouldn't have any luck.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.42,0:50:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我真希望尼奇與他那票人 可以馬上消失\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: I wished Nicky and his whole crew would just get lost.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.50,0:50:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,但我能怎樣？ 回老家去挑起場戰爭？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}What am I gonna do? Go back home and start a war?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.01,0:50:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,尼奇在幫媞漎O有頭有臉的人物 我不能那麼做\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Nicky's a made guy and I'm not. I can't do that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.80,0:50:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,到處都是賭博遊樂公會的探員\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Gaming agents are all over the place.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.93,0:50:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,這兒不允許手氣旺的人嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I'm not allowed to get lucky in this place?{\r}
