Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.69,1:01:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,-是，別擔心 -好的，謝啦\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-Yes. Don't worry. -All right. Thanks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.20,1:01:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我們在整城堻ㄕ魚u民 從旅館侍者…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: He had tipsters all over town. Bellmen...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.91,1:01:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,-得快點 -好的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-You got to hurry. -Okay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.04,1:01:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,-停車小弟… -他們正在登記\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-...valet parkers... -They're just checking in now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.62,1:01:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-我會告訴他 -賭區經理…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-I'll tell him. -...pit bosses...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.29,1:01:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,在西洛可的1230房\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Room 1230 at the Scirocco.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.63,1:01:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-1230房，收到 -還有秘書\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-1 230. Right. -...secretaries.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.63,1:01:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-完美狀況的硬幣 -完美狀況嗎？收到\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-Mint condition coins. -Mint condition? All right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.43,1:01:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他們當然都有一份\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: They all got a piece of the score.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.30,1:01:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,車來了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}MAN: Car's coming.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.35,1:01:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他們都很謹慎\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: They were very careful.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.40,1:01:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他們每次都先解除警鈴 要不然…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}They always bypassed the alarms, or else, if not...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.69,1:01:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,就在牆上打洞然後鑿牆而入\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}they'd drill enough holes to knock through the walls with a sledgehammer.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.87,1:01:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,尼奇能偷的都偷了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Nicky was grabbing everything he could.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.70,1:01:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,外頭根本沒有人想到 會有像他那樣的人\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Nobody out there was expecting a guy like him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.08,1:01:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,對尼奇來說 拉斯維加斯就像是蠻荒西部\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}For Nicky, Las Vegas was the fucking Wild West.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.96,1:01:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我才剛拿到一批從以色列來的鑽石\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I just got a shipment of diamonds from Israel.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.17,1:01:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,他們他媽的想要我怎樣？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: What the fuck did they expect from me?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.90,1:01:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我得賺錢，不是嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I had to earn, didn't I?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.22,1:02:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,-這些鑽石有瑕疵 -沒有瑕疵\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-This diamond has flaws in it. -There's no flaws in it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.52,1:02:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,別告訴我怎麼做 我在這行已經25年了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Don't tell me. I'm doing this for 25 years.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.48,1:02:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你的放大鏡最好擦乾淨點 因為這批鑽石沒有瑕疵\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You better clean your loupe, because there's no flaws in this diamond.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.86,1:02:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,通常要是附近來的貨…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: When we got local merch...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.57,1:02:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我們都會送到棕櫚泉市 或是亞利桑那州與洛杉磯\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}we'd usually send it to Palm Springs, or Arizona, L.A.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.28,1:02:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我有幾個熟識的中東佬 你知道，阿拉伯人\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I had a couple of sand niggers out there. You know, Arabs.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.16,1:02:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你們是要開會還是要買鑽石？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Are you gonna have a meeting or buy some diamonds?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.79,1:02:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我懂他的語言，我跟他講講\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I know his language. I'm talking with him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.08,1:02:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,全部四萬塊\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}$40,000, you buy the whole package.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.04,1:02:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,兩萬，不要拉倒\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}$20,000. That's my final offer.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.25,1:02:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他突然會說英文了 別玩遊戲了，兩萬五\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He suddenly talks English. Let's talk turkey. $25,000.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.72,1:02:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我將我的房間改為保險箱 保留一些我特選的好東西\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: I actually turned my bedroom into a bank vault where I kept the choice stuff.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.27,1:02:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,因為員警可能會突然臨檢 所以不能將其留在店堙K\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I couldn't leave it at the Gold Rush in case we got raided by the cops...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.90,1:02:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,也防止我手下手癢\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}or if my crew got cute.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.19,1:02:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我保有唯一的鑰匙 珍妮佛才不在乎\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I had the only key. Jennifer didn't give a fuck.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.40,1:02:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,她每晚都在沙發上 看電影看到睡著\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}She fell asleep on the couch watching TV every night.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.78,1:02:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,這些全是我的東西 我一樣也沒送回老家\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}This stuff was all mine. I didn't send any of this back home.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.66,1:02:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,其實我也不行 因為我根本不應該做這些\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Actually, I couldn't, because I wasn't supposed to be doing it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.87,1:03:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,老大們光是賭場就賺飽了…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}The bosses were making so much money with the casinos...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.54,1:03:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他們不希望有人惹是非\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}that they didn't want anybody making any waves.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.05,1:03:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你的人馬每人都分到了嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You've all given your crew a piece of that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.26,1:03:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我大家都罩好了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I took care of everybody.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.10,1:03:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是為什麼在我來之前 拉斯維加斯並沒有犯罪集團\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: That's why there was no real organized street stuff in Vegas before I came.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.10,1:03:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,但我家衣櫃堣S能藏多少錢呢？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}But how much cash could I bury in my closet, right?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.86,1:03:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你必須要瞭解 而我也相信你瞭解…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You have to understand, and I'm sure you do...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.03,1:03:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,做這種風險大的投資…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}that in a venture of this kind...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.82,1:03:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,要有可能虧損的心理準備\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}you must be prepared to take some kind of loss.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.70,1:03:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我將一些錢交給查理克拉克 艾斯的銀行經理，做一些正當投資\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: I put some money in legitimate deals with Charlie Clark, Ace's banker.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.58,1:03:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-你會盡力而為，不是嗎？ -是的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-You will try to push it through, won't you? -Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.21,1:03:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你得瞭解我現在 給了你五萬元現金\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You got to understand, I'm giving you $50,000 cash.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.54,1:03:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,然後我將更多錢投入正當的投資 例如我開的餐館\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: Then I put more money in some legitimate places, like my restaurant.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.34,1:03:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-剩這個了？ -是\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}DOMINICK: Is that the last one? COOK: Yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.93,1:03:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我讓我小弟，多明尼可經營\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: I had my kid brother, Dominick, run it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.56,1:03:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,王八蛋\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Fuckers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.77,1:03:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,在這傜N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}DOMINICK: Here you go, guys.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.27,1:03:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-謝了 -慢慢享用\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-Thanks a lot. -Enjoy it. Have a good time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.94,1:03:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,-噎死你，王八蛋 -嗨，小多\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-Choke on it, motherfucker. -Hi, Dom.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.82,1:03:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼樣？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}How you doing?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.20,1:04:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，尼奇很喜歡餐館 他對開餐廳也很拿手\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Yeah, Nicky loved restaurants. He was a real restaurant buff.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.20,1:04:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼多年來，他逢開餐廳必賺\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}And over the years, he always made money with them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.92,1:04:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他在拉斯維加斯開了比薩斜塔 很受大家歡迎\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}In Vegas, he had the Leaning Tower. It was a very popular spot.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.42,1:04:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,常有政客、脫衣舞娘 還有電影明星光顧\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He had politicians, showgirls and movie stars hanging out all over.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.93,1:04:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,佛羅明哥的那場秀越做越好羅\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}That show at The Flamingo gets better and better.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.35,1:04:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,對了，山姆說 請你有空時打個電話給他\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}By the way, Sammy said whenever you have a minute, give him a call.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.02,1:04:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-你也變傳話的了啊？ -有錢我什麼都做啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-Made you a messenger, too? -I'll do anything for a buck.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.69,1:04:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-他對每個人都這樣，好好享用晚餐 -謝啦\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-He does it to everybody. Enjoy your dinner. -Thanks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.19,1:04:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,尼奇最喜歡的 當然就是脫衣舞娘\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: I got to tell you, the thing Nicky liked most was the showgirls.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.03,1:04:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,對她們來說，尼奇像是電影名星\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}To them, Nicky was the movie star.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.24,1:04:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-你就這樣走過？ -這是雪麗\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-You walk past me? -This is Shelly.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.20,1:04:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,-嗨，雪麗，你好嗎？ -嗨\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-Hi, Shelly. How are you? -Hi.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.25,1:04:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,這是史黛希\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}This is Stacy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.04,1:04:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-這是尼克，想吃晚餐嗎？一起吧 -好啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-This is Nick. Wanna have dinner? Come on. -All right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.21,1:04:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我帶你去廚房看看 失陪一下\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Let's check the kitchen first. Excuse us one second.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.80,1:04:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧，我帶你去 我每天都空運新鮮的東西進來\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: Come on, I'll show you. I fly stuff in fresh every day.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.43,1:04:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我從老家運麵包 從加州運魚\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I get bread from back home. I get fish from California.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.81,1:04:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,光從我們用奶餵食的小牛肉就看得出 我們絕對是好餐廳\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You can always tell a great kitchen like ours because of the milk-fed veal.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.60,1:04:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是訣竅 奶喂小牛的肉是純白色的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}That's the secret. See, milk-fed veal is pure white.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.61,1:04:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,其他餐館都用那種粉紅色的小牛肉 過去點，甜心\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Out here, they got that pink veal. Slide over, honey.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.90,1:05:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,粉紅色的那種小牛肉 你就算是追個兩天兩夜\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Now, pink veal you can pound for two days.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.24,1:05:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,它還是不會變嫩 你懂我的意思嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: It'll never ever get tender. You know what I mean?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.79,1:05:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我從這兒拿錢離開時 在街上被搶了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}AL: I left here with the money. Got muscled on the street.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.92,1:05:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是幾個我欠錢的傢伙 所以我把錢給他們了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}A couple guys, I owe them. So I gave them the money.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.25,1:05:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-就是這樣 -是嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-That's what I did. -Yeah?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.63,1:05:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你還敢自稱是男人嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You call yourself a man?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.47,1:05:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道你是個撒謊的雜碎 他媽的爛賭的狗東西嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You know you're a lying lowlife, motherfucking gambling degenerate prick?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.93,1:05:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道自己是什麼東西嗎？ 家埵釣潃茪p孩\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You know that's what you are? Two small kids at home.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.77,1:05:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我給你錢付房租…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I gave you money to pay the fucking rent...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.81,1:05:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,買菜、開暖氣\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}and buy groceries, put the heat on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.11,1:05:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道你老婆打給法蘭克 說家堻s暖氣都被停了嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You know your wife called Frankie and told him the fucking heat's off?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.61,1:05:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒拿錢去賭嗎？ 你敢這樣跟我說嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You didn't gamble that money? Can you tell me that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.16,1:05:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-你沒有嗎？ -沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-No, you didn't? -I didn't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.87,1:05:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,別耍我，艾爾！ 別把我當傻子\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Don't fuck with me, Al! Don't make a fuck out of me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.50,1:05:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你當我是傻子是吧？ 你沒去賭？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You wanna make a fool out of me? You didn't gamble?{\r}
