Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.97,1:10:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他們每天24小時都在想著 怎麼將我搶空\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}They're all looking to rob me blind 24 hours a day.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.81,1:10:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我必須要讓他們知道 我隨時都在注意每個細節\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I have to let them know I'm watching all the details all the time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.14,1:10:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會漏掉任何一樣事情\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}That there is not one single thing I will not catch.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.40,1:11:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,看你的，看\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Look at yours. Look at that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.32,1:11:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,再看這個，什麼都沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Look at this. There's nothing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.49,1:11:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你看你的藍莓那麼多\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Look how many blueberries your muffin has.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.58,1:11:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-我一個都沒有 -你在說什麼？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-I have nothing. -What are you talking about?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.37,1:11:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,自己不動手做就弄不好\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}If you don't do it yourself, it never gets done.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.33,1:11:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去哪兒？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}PHILIP: Where are you going?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.50,1:11:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,從現在開始 我要你全都放同份量的藍莓\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: From now on, I want you to put an equal amount of blueberries in each muffin.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.81,1:11:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道那多花時間嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Do you know how long that will take?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.60,1:11:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我不管要多久 每個松餅的份量都要一致\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I don't care how long it takes. Put an equal amount in each muffin.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.78,1:11:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,再吃一點，乖\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Just a little. That a girl.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.87,1:11:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-你要找媽媽？ -來媽媽這兒？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Wanna go to Mommy? GINGER: Wanna come to Mommy?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.99,1:11:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，甜心\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}It's all right, sweetheart.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.00,1:11:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我要跟你談談，我需要點錢\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}GINGER: I need to talk to you. I need some money.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.13,1:11:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-你要什麼？ -抱好了嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-What do you need? -Got her?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.05,1:11:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要很多，比平時要多\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I need a lot. I need more than usual.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.47,1:11:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼不從你戶頭領呢？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Why don't you take it out of your account?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.72,1:11:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我本想，只是…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I would, it's just that...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.73,1:12:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要更多，我要兩萬五\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I need more than that. I need $25,000.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.31,1:12:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,兩萬五千元？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}$25,000?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.94,1:12:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,-你自己要？ -是啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-For yourself? -Yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.57,1:12:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你為什麼要那麼多？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Why do you need that much?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.74,1:12:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼差別？我需要就是了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}What's the difference? I just need it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.41,1:12:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定得問啊 那很多錢耶，又不只是一盒爆米花\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I gotta ask you. That's a lot of money. It's not a box of popcorn.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.16,1:12:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我們不用將這變成件大事\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}We don't have to turn this into a big deal.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.75,1:12:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我們不用吵架\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}We don't have to have a fight.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.80,1:12:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,只是對我很重要，算了 有些想做的事罷了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}GINGER: It was important to me. Forget it. Something I wanted to do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.09,1:12:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,誰在吵架？ 告訴我錢的用處\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Who's fighting? Tell me what it's for.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.85,1:12:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼不能告訴我？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Why can't you tell me what it's for?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.98,1:12:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,現在我要你告訴我\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Now I want you to tell me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.03,1:12:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我老婆跑來問我要兩萬五 你想買大衣嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}My wife comes to me and asks me for $25,000. Do you want a coat?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.03,1:12:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-不 -如果想買大衣，就去買啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}GINGER: No. SAM: If you want a coat, you got it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.54,1:12:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不是錢的問題 只是，你為什麼要？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}It's not the money. It's just, why do you want it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.29,1:12:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我無權過問嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Am I not entitled to ask that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.00,1:12:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我一輩子都很獨立 我從不為任何事求人\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I've been independent all my life. I never had to ask anybody for anything.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.63,1:12:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,現在你要我求你是吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Now you're making me beg you for this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.13,1:13:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,-你在說什麼？ -好，你還羞辱我\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-What are you talking about? -Okay? And you're embarrassing me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.14,1:13:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-為什麼得讓我如此難受？ -你問我要兩萬五\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Why make me feel so bad? SAM: You're asking me for $25,000.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.10,1:13:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是要讓你難堪 我只是希望能信任你\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I'm not out to make you feel bad. I want to just be able to trust you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.98,1:13:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是信任問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}It's about trust.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.81,1:13:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我必須要連性命都能交托於你\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I have to be able to trust you with my life.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.19,1:13:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Do you understand?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.07,1:13:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我能信任你嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Can I trust you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.21,1:13:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我能嗎？告訴我\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Can I trust you? Answer me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.21,1:13:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你能\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You can trust me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.42,1:13:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好，那你就可以告訴我 錢要拿來幹嘛\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Good. So then you can tell me what the money is for.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.04,1:13:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,她現在正離開銀行\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}She's leaving the bank now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.96,1:14:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟著她\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I'll follow her.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.46,1:14:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}LESTER: What is that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.59,1:14:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道那神情，那表情是什麼意思？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I know that look. What does that look mean?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.63,1:14:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,意思是我有錢\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}GINGER: It means I got the money.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.41,1:14:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你好嗎？是萊斯特吧？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}How are you doing? It's Lester, right?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.63,1:14:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我記得你不是玩牌老手…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}From my recollection, aren't you the card shark...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.68,1:14:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,高爾夫球騙子 比佛利山莊的皮條客嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}the golf hustler, the pimp from Beverly Hills?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.27,1:14:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,若記錯了，請糾正我\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: If I'm wrong, correct me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.85,1:14:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我從不知道你也是個小偷\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I never knew you to be a heist man.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.69,1:14:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不過如果是的話，這樣吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}But if you are, you know what?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.61,1:14:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我的也拿去吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Here, take mine, too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.78,1:14:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,拿吧，反正你已拿了她的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Take it. You already have hers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.49,1:15:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,她是我老婆\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}She's my wife.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.87,1:15:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,看著我\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Look at me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.04,1:15:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吧？ 你知道她是我老婆吧？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You did know that, didn't you? You knew she's my wife?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.04,1:15:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-看著我 -我知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Look at me. LESTER: I know that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.67,1:15:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,知道啊？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: You do, yeah?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.01,1:15:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你下次若再想回來…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}If you ever come back again...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.14,1:15:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,拿她的錢，記得帶槍\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}to take her money, next time bring a pistol.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.02,1:15:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣你才有機會\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}That way you got a chance.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.94,1:15:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,當個男人，別做皮條客\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Be a man, don't be a fucking pimp.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.27,1:15:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,現在，賣我個面子 快滾吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Now, you want to do me a favor? Get out of here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.15,1:15:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我想跟我老婆獨處 給我他媽的滾\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I wanna be alone with my wife. Get the fuck up and get out of here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.46,1:15:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,渾蛋狗雜種\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Fucking piece of shit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.77,1:15:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,記得那晚你打電話跟他道別嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Remember when you called him that night and said goodbye to him?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.19,1:15:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,他並沒說：   “別結婚，我馬上來”\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He didn't say, "Don't get married. I'll be right down."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.11,1:16:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,-他沒這樣說吧？ -不，沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-He didn't say that, did he? -No, he didn't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.23,1:16:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那他說了什麼？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}What did he say?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.11,1:16:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,“跟他睡，撈光他的錢”\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}"Fuck him. Take him for everything he's got."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.87,1:16:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,過來，我給你看樣東西\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Come here. I want to show you something.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.72,1:16:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,叫他們停！\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}GINGER: Make them stop it!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.07,1:16:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不是他的錯！是我的錯！\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}It's not his fault! It's my fault!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.42,1:16:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,沒用的狗雜種\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}THUG: Piece of shit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.02,1:17:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,自己來吧，你這沒膽的渾蛋！\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}LESTER: Do it yourself, you chickenshit cocksucker!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.15,1:17:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他太可惡了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He's such a prick.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.11,1:17:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他叫旅館的人揍他\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He had some guy from the hotel beat him up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.15,1:17:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他自己不想動手\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He didn't want to do it himself.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.36,1:17:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他不想將手弄髒\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He didn't want to get his own hands dirty.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.29,1:17:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他為什麼要這樣？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Why did he have to do that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.46,1:17:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,告訴我\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Tell me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.79,1:17:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-那不是件好事… -廢話\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: It wasn't a nice thing to do-- GINGER: No shit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.46,1:17:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你得瞭解，\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You gotta understand it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.30,1:17:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他並不知道這人 是不是在騙你的錢\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He doesn't know if this guy is shaking you down.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.47,1:17:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我在結婚前就告訴過他這個人了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I told him all about this guy before we got married.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.31,1:17:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-這並不是什麼新鮮事 -是嗎？我並不知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-This is no fucking surprise. -You did? I didn't know that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.02,1:17:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他只是我的朋友 我想要幫他，有什麼大不了？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He's just a friend of mine I was trying to help. So what?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.15,1:17:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我第一次看到你們倆在一起時…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}The first time I ever saw you guys together...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.49,1:17:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我從未見他那麼快樂過\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I never saw him so happy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.91,1:17:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道他是個猶太瘋子…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: I know he's a crazy Jew fuck and everything...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.99,1:17:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,但我從未見過他跟別人一起時這樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}but I never seen him act like that with anybody else.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.58,1:17:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,他為你瘋狂 他真的很愛你\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I think he's crazy about you. He really loves you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.67,1:17:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,-他真的是 -拜託\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: He does. GINGER: Come on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.71,1:18:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我是睜著雙眼走進這關係的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I went into this with my eyes open.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.93,1:18:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道隨時都可能變卦\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}GINGER: I knew the bottom could drop out any time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.35,1:18:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我也混過，你真以為 我在沒有保障的情況下…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I'm a working girl. You don't think I'm gonna go into a situation like this...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.18,1:18:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,會走這條路嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}if I don't think I'm covered on the back end?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.56,1:18:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，我可以瞭解\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Sure, I can see that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.69,1:18:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他買了好多珠寶給我 好多好多\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}So he put aside some jewelry for me. A lot of jewelry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.40,1:18:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,很多貴重的珠寶？ 大概值多少？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}A lot of expensive jewelry? About how much?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.49,1:18:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你想偷嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You want to steal it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.45,1:18:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不，只是好奇 我是在想…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}No. I'm just curious. I was wondering...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.71,1:18:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他會在那種東西 投入多少錢\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}how much he would put into a thing like that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.25,1:18:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他跟我說大約一百萬 可能更多\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I'm told it's worth about $1 million, maybe more.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.38,1:18:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是羅 這說明了什麼？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: There you go. What does that tell you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.72,1:18:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,一百萬的珠寶\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}$1 million in jewelry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.89,1:18:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,這不說明了他愛你愛到瘋了嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Does that tell you he is crazy about you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.10,1:18:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我根本就不該嫁給他的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I should have never married him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.73,1:18:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,他是雙子座的，雙子加三級，兩面人\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He's a Gemini. Triple Gemini. Duality.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.02,1:18:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,雙子座就像條蛇 你不能相信蛇\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Gemini is the snake, you know. You can't trust a snake.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.15,1:18:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我說真的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I mean it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.49,1:18:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我懂你的意思，金吉兒，聽著\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I know what you mean. Listen, Ginger.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.29,1:18:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,這可能不是… 我也沒有答案\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}This is probably not.... I don't have the answers anyway.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.12,1:19:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-這可能不是你想聽的 -我想\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-This is probably not what you want to hear. -I do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.46,1:19:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你不高興，我可以理解…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You're a little upset, and I understand that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.26,1:19:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,但先撐著點吧 慢慢來，看看會發生什麼事\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}But try to make the best of it now. Go slow. See what happens.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.59,1:19:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,他差點殺了他！\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He could've killed him!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.60,1:19:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他用不著打他 我又沒跟他上床\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He didn't have to hit him. I'm not sleeping with the guy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.85,1:19:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他讓我得偷偷摸摸的 跟我的朋友見面\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He makes me sneak around to see my own friends.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.15,1:19:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,這算什麼呢？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}What the fuck is that all about?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.61,1:19:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我想是因為他太愛你了吧 他吃醋又擔心\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I guess it's 'cause he loves you so much, he's jealous and worries.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.45,1:19:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,誰會在乎我做什麼？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Who gives a fuck what I do?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.20,1:19:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我會試著問問到底怎樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I'll try to find out what the hell is going on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.62,1:19:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,-遇到他時我會跟他談談的 -好\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-When I see him, I'll talk to him. -Okay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.29,1:19:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-可以嗎？ -好\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-All right? -Yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.21,1:19:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,謝了…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Thanks...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.51,1:19:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,忍受我嘮叨\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}for putting up with me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.22,1:19:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,別喝這麼凶吧 這只會讓情況更糟\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Take it easy with this shit. This can only make matters worse.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.93,1:19:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你是個美女，別搞砸了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You're a beautiful girl. Don't ruin that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.97,1:19:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我看過太多漂亮女孩 因這個變醜八怪\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I've seen a lot of girls get shot to hell from this stuff.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.98,1:19:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你真好\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You're so nice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.98,1:19:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好了啦 我不想見你不快樂\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Come on, now. I don't wanna see you unhappy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.40,1:19:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,謝了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Thanks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.33,1:20:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事啦\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}It's all right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.97,1:20:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,縣輔導派特委布來見你\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}County Commissioner Pat Webb is here to see you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.43,1:20:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-等一下 -好的，請稍候\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-Give me a minute. -Okay. Just a minute.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.38,1:20:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要什麼嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}RECEPTIONIST: Can I get you anything?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.96,1:20:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不，謝謝，小姐\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}No, thank you, little lady.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.22,1:20:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,讓他進來，然後四分鐘後打給我\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Send him in and call me four minutes after.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.88,1:20:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,羅斯坦先生，我是派特委布\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Mr. Rothstein, I'm Pat Webb.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.22,1:20:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你好嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}How do you do?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.31,1:20:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-幸會 -我常聽起你的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-It is a pleasure. -I heard a lot about you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.43,1:20:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,過獎了，莊家最近還過得去\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}PAT: Thank you, sir. House is doing well.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.06,1:21:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼多錢滾滾而來\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}All that money is rolling in.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.40,1:21:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我很感激你願意見我這老公僕\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I appreciate you taking the time to see a poor old civil servant.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.49,1:21:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-不如坐下吧？ -謝謝您\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Why don't you have a seat? PAT: Thank you, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.03,1:21:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我是來親自化解…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}PAT: I come here personally to smooth over...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.33,1:21:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,一些小誤會的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}any fracas about a certain matter.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.92,1:21:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你可能不知道…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Maybe you didn't know it...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.79,1:21:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,但道恩華德在鎮上挺受歡迎的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}but Don Ward is a very well-liked man in this town.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.05,1:21:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他有許多朋友 他們家族及產業也很久了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He's got lots of friends. His family and their money go back many years.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.64,1:21:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,朋友是選民 家人與金錢都能助選\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Friends vote, family and money votes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.27,1:21:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,這對你我都很重要\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}That's important to me and you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.27,1:21:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,若你從這個角度 來看我們這個小問題的話…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}If you'll think about our little problem along them lines...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.86,1:21:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉我得這麼說…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}and you'll forgive me for saying it...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.07,1:21:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但他可能不該被開除\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}maybe he did not deserve to be fired.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.62,1:21:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他非常清楚我們…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He knew about our getting hit...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.62,1:21:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,在一瞬間被贏了三個大獎 但他卻袖手旁觀\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}on three big machines in a row, and he did nothing about it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.79,1:21:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他要不是跟他們一夥 那很抱歉，他就是蠢到看不見\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Either he was in on it or, forgive me, he was too dumb to see it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.80,1:21:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不論如何，我都無法讓一個 這樣的人在這兒工作\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Either way, I cannot have a man like that working here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.30,1:21:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,在將過錯都推給道恩前…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Before we point the dirty end of the stick at old Don...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.84,1:22:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我們得先確定有證據這樣指控他\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}we better be sure we can prove them charges.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.56,1:22:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我，要是有證據 他早就被逮捕了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Believe me, if I could prove it, he'd be under arrest.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.69,1:22:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你確定要讓賭博遊樂委員會…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Are we certain that you want the Gaming Control Board...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.57,1:22:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,過目你與你的幫派朋友 尼奇的記錄嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}eyeballing your record and your gangster pals like Nicky?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.16,1:22:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得你這樣跟我說 有點太過份了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I think you're way out of line talking to me like that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.83,1:22:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你所說的幾乎是譭謗 你無權懷疑我的專業\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}What you're saying is libelous. You're in no position to challenge my expertise.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.37,1:22:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我已盡我所能去 幫助並善待那孩子\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I went way out of my way to be helpful and courteous to that kid.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.84,1:22:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他太弱了也很無能 他使這地方瀕於險境\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He's weak. He's incompetent. He jeopardizes the whole place.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.34,1:22:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我對他真的無能為力\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}There's not much more I can do for him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.51,1:22:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,這倒是真的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You have got me there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.35,1:22:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,道恩就像公豬身上的乳頭一樣無用\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Old Don is as useless as tits on a boar.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.89,1:22:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但他還是我的小舅子…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}But he is my brother-in-law...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.61,1:22:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我會當是我欠你的一個人情\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}and I would look on it as a personal favor...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.36,1:22:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,若你願意考慮重新聘用他\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}if you'd think some more on hiring him back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.53,1:22:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I can't do that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.70,1:22:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道他是你的小舅子\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I appreciate the fact that he's your brother-in-law.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.41,1:22:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想幫你更喜歡賣人情\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I do want to help you and I like to do favors.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.79,1:22:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我也知道你的地位 但我真的不能這麼做\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}And I know who you are. But I cannot do that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.42,1:23:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,日後是否會有其他較適合的…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Could there be any position...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.47,1:23:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,職位呢？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}farther down the trough?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.81,1:23:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉，並沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I'm sorry. I can't do anything.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.22,1:23:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他太無能了 最終還是他不能被信任\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He's too incompetent. The bottom line is he cannot be trusted.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.94,1:23:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，謝謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Okay, thanks a lot.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.70,1:23:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}That's it. I'm sorry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.12,1:23:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,羅斯坦先生 你們這幫人永遠都不會懂…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Mr. Rothstein, your people never will understand...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.29,1:23:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,這堛漸@界如何運作\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}the way it works out here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.42,1:23:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你們只不過來此地做客\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You're all just our guests.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.13,1:23:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,但卻喧寶奪主\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}But you act like you're at home.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.30,1:23:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我告訴你，老兄 這並不是你家\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Let me tell you something, partner. You ain't home.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.30,1:23:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,家是我們州長生氣時 送你們回的地方\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}But that's where we'll send you if it harelips the Governor.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.64,1:23:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-多謝你空出時間見我 -沒問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-Thank you for your time. -No problem.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.44,1:23:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-對不起 -當然\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-Sorry. -You bet.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.62,1:23:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我的藥呢？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: What happened to my pills?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.87,1:24:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你喝那麼多酒還不夠嗎？ 你還要吃我的藥？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Isn't it bad enough you drink too much? You're taking my pills, too?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.29,1:24:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒吃你的藥\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}GINGER: I didn't take your pills.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.92,1:24:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我因為胃潰瘍，才吃半顆\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}For my ulcer, I take a half of one of these.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.13,1:24:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,而且是痛到無法忍時才吃\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}That's when I have extreme pain.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.72,1:24:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我本來有三個月份的 你弄到哪里去了？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I had a three-month supply. What did you do with them?{\r}
