Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.63,1:25:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你下定決心的事 你就做得比任何人都要好\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}When you set your mind on doing something, you do it better than anybody.{\r}
