Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.90,1:27:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,遺漏，狗屁 我要找到搶我們的人\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Leakage, my balls. I want the guy who's robbing us.{\r}
