Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.85,1:40:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,對我來說時期最壞不過\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}And at the worst possible time for me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.23,1:40:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我的執照聽證會要到了 我不想有一點點失敗的機率\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I had my license hearing coming up and I didn't want to leave anything to chance.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.98,1:40:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,若不能在賭城工作 那我要去哪兒？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}If I can't work in Vegas, where am I gonna go?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.32,1:40:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直都很合作 從檔到帳簿\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You've been very open with us with the books and papers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.03,1:40:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,這對委員會是很重要的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}That'll mean a lot when you go before the commission.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.66,1:40:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,-我只希望能有個公正的聽證會 -你的誠實會為你贏的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-All I ask is a fair hearing. -This honesty will guarantee it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:52.91,1:40:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}We'll move on to....{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.04,1:40:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我想聽聽關於堪薩斯市\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: I want to hear about Kansas City.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.26,1:41:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,這他媽的是什麼？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}What the fuck is this?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.30,1:41:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,這傢伙要停在哪里，球場上嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Where's this fucking guy gonna land, in the fairway?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:28.08,1:41:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他們是探員，法蘭克 來看看\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}They're fucking agents, Frankie. Look at this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.46,1:41:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他們盯尼奇打高爾夫盯到…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: The Feds were watching Nicky play golf for so long...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:35.17,1:41:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,飛機沒油\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}they ran out of gas.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:37.92,1:41:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,還真是我需要的 就在委員會面前\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Just what I needed, right in front of the control board.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.89,1:41:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,賭一百看誰先打到飛機\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}$100, whoever hits the plane.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.85,1:41:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,禍不單行，隨後就看到派斯康 堪薩斯市的老二\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: If things weren't bad enough... in comes Piscano, the Kansas City underboss.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.32,1:41:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,在堪薩斯市收皮箱的那家超市 就是他開的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He ran the grocery store in Kansas City where they brought the suitcases.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:58.94,1:42:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,又在為皮箱的事吵了 你知道這代表什麼嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Fighting over those suitcases again. You know what that means?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.28,1:42:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我又得去拉斯維加斯了 又要花我好幾千\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I gotta take another trip to Vegas. It's gonna cost me another couple grand.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:05.95,1:42:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他和他姐夫一起開店…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: He ran it with his brother-in-law...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:07.54,1:42:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,但他大多都在跟他姐夫與岳母 抱怨他去賭城的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}but he mostly complained about his trips to Vegas to his brother-in-law and mother.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:12.04,1:42:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你得表明態度 要不然他們當你是病貓\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You gotta lay down the law, or they'll make a fool out of you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:15.59,1:42:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我全記下來了，他媽的每一分一毛\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I write it all down. Every fucking nickel goes down.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:19.26,1:42:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-你是怎麼了？ -全都在這兒\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-What's the matter with you? -Everything's here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:23.01,1:42:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-你何時開始這樣講話？ -抱歉\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-Since when do you talk like that? -I'm sorry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.14,1:42:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,南斯要是找我麻煩 我就將他的眼挖出來\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Nance gives me trouble, I'll take the eyes out of his freaking head.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.73,1:42:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,-又來了 -我沒罵粗話\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-Again. -I didn't curse, I said, "freaking head."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.19,1:42:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-夠了 -抱歉\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-That's enough. -I'm sorry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:33.48,1:42:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來發生的事 簡直是出乎意料\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: What happens next, you can't believe it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.78,1:42:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,誰會想到聯邦調查局 會在堶掘侜捇札飽K\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Who'd believe the FBI had a wire in the place...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:38.70,1:42:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,為了調查很久以前的一樁命案…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}looking for information about some old homicide...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.45,1:42:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,為了一個不知在何時 也不知為何事被幹掉的人\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}about some guy who was whacked out God knows when over God knows what?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:44.87,1:42:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼阻止拿皮箱的人 拿走他想要的？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}What prevents him with the suitcases from taking what he wants?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:48.00,1:42:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,南斯從坦吉樂拿了兩口箱子回來\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Nance brings back two suitcases from the Tangiers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:50.25,1:42:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,若其實有三箱或四箱呢？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}What about three or four?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.04,1:42:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我們沒有人在計算室堿搧 那是法律\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}We've got nobody in the room to watch. That's the law.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:55.05,1:42:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我們甚至連計算室都進不去\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}We can't even go into the count room to watch our money.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.76,1:43:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他有他的人在堶 他們搞不好根本是一夥的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He's got his people in there. They could all be in on it together.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:04.10,1:43:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,若我知道是葛林幹的 我會埋了那王八蛋\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I'll find out. If it's Green himself, I'll bury that bastard.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:07.39,1:43:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我從就不相信他 我後腦都有眼睛\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I never trusted him. I got eyes behind my head.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.06,1:43:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他們信任那渾蛋，我可不\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}They trust that scumbag. I don't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:11.86,1:43:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我該給他們一人一鏟\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I'll hit the two of them in the head with a shovel.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:14.28,1:43:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,冷靜點\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}MA: Take it easy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.44,1:43:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,媽，抱歉 但他們一直跟我玩陰的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Ma, I'm sorry. They're beating me left and right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.32,1:43:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-抱歉，我很生氣 -我知道，可是夠了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}ARTIE: I'm sorry. I'm upset. I know, but that's enough.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:20.74,1:43:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你也知道他們在對我做什麼 我受不了了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You know what they're doing to me. I can't take this no more.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:24.04,1:43:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-冷靜，別心臟病發 -我知道，我太氣了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}MA: Take it easy. You'll get a heart attack. ARTIE: I know. I'm too upset.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.92,1:43:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,該死的是，他們聽得一清二楚…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: The damn thing is, they hear all this stuff...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.21,1:43:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,關於拉斯維加斯，賭場還有皮箱…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}about Las Vegas, casinos, and suitcases...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:34.59,1:43:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,玩完了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}and that's it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:41.72,1:43:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,全都是從我口袋堭 我得付錢\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}ARTIE: Everything's coming out of my pocket. I gotta pay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:45.89,1:43:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你相信有這麼巧嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Would you believe this could happen?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:47.60,1:43:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,華府
Dialogue: 0,1:43:48.98,1:43:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我是來賺錢的，不是虧錢\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}ARTIE: I'm in this to make money, not lose it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.98,1:43:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,全國每個聯邦調查局探員 都張大了耳朵\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Every FBI man across the country had their ears open now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:54.82,1:43:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,要將事情辦好就得靠自己\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}ARTIE: If you want something done right you gotta do it yourself.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:58.87,1:44:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,派司康這傢伙 幾乎搞砸了所有人的生活\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Piscano, this guy, basically sunk the whole world.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:03.83,1:44:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,有些好的就有些壞的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}MA: There are some that are good and some that are bad.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:06.79,1:44:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,1980年
Dialogue: 0,1:44:07.88,1:44:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,主席先生 委員會的同仁…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}COUNSELOR: Members of the Commission...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:09.84,1:44:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,今天羅斯坦先生很榮幸能在這兒\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Mr. Rothstein is pleased to be here today.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:11.84,1:44:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,當那天終於來時 我已準備好了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: When the day finally came, I was ready.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.30,1:44:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我自信滿滿的認為 我只需要呈上我的案件\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I felt so confident that all I had to do was present my case.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.22,1:44:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我們擁有檔，其中一份是由 一位退休的聯邦探員寫的…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}COUNSELOR: We have documents, one of which is a report by retired FBl agents...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:22.81,1:44:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,上頭清楚的記載羅斯坦先生 並未觸犯任何法律\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}which completely absolves Mr. Rothstein from any wrongdoing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.23,1:44:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-律師，在你繼續前… -我要將這呈為…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-Counselor, before you continue... -I want to have this marked....{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:29.82,1:44:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,本委員會針對是否應 駁回羅斯坦的申請書在此動議\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}...this Commission acts on a motion denying the Rothstein application.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:34.07,1:44:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-駁回？ -有人贊成駁回嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}COUNSELOR: Denying? SENATOR: Do I hear a motion seconded?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.20,1:44:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,主席先生，我贊成\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Mr. Chairman, I second the motion.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:38.99,1:44:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,還有贊同票嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Do I have a vote on the motion?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:40.74,1:44:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,同意！\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-Aye! -Aye!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:43.21,1:44:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,同意票獲勝，聽證會結束\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}The ayes have it. This hearing is adjourned.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:45.29,1:44:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-開什麼玩笑 -什麼叫結束？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-You have to be kidding. -Adjourned? What do you mean?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:49.25,1:44:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,議員，你答應我一場聽證會的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Senator, you promised me a hearing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:51.61,1:44:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你連聯邦調查局的報告都沒看\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You didn't even look at the FBl reports.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:54.05,1:44:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你來坦吉樂作客時\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}When you were my guest at the Tangiers Hotel,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:56.96,1:44:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不是答應我會有公平的聽證會？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}didn't you promise me a fair hearing?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:59.31,1:45:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-我從未是你的客人\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SENATOR: I was never your guest.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:00.72,1:45:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-不是我的客人？我沒招待過你？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Never my guest? I never comped you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:02.98,1:45:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,難道我一個月 沒有最少招待你三次？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I don't comp you at least three times a month?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:05.40,1:45:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在回答這個問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I'd like to answer that at this time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.82,1:45:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,羅斯坦先生的反應很常見 他在撒謊\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Mr. Rothstein is being very typical to this point. He's lying.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:11.19,1:45:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我唯一一次去過坦吉樂 就是巴尼葛林斯坦那次晚宴\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}The only time I was at the Tangiers was a dinner with Barney Greenstein.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:15.24,1:45:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-我當時在場嗎？ -你四處周旋著\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Was I at the dinner? SENATOR: You were wandering around.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:18.03,1:45:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,-我在場嗎？ -你四處周旋\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Was I at that dinner? SENATOR: You were wandering.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:21.16,1:45:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,-你在室內 -我在室內？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SENATOR: You were in the building. SAM: I was in the building?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.29,1:45:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你很清楚我在那兒\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You know damn well I was there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:26.01,1:45:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你向我保證會有公正的聽證會\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You swore I would have a fair hearing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:29.09,1:45:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Did you not?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.88,1:45:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,至少承認說我那天在場 這總可以了吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Tell me I was at least at the dinner. Allow me that much.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.85,1:45:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-至少也得說我在場吧！ -是，你在\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Give me that much at least! SENATOR: Yes, you were.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:39.43,1:45:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,多謝你沒說我是騙子 你這個狗東西\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Thanks for not calling me a liar, you son of a bitch.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:44.40,1:45:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,一場例行的聽證會 在昨晚成了一場鬧劇…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}A routine licensing hearing turned into bedlam yesterday...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:47.90,1:45:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,當搶眼的坦吉樂高層 山姆“艾斯”羅斯坦…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}when the flamboyant Tangiers Casino executive, Sam "Ace" Rothstein...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:51.70,1:45:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,指控賭博遊樂委員會高官貪污\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}accused top gaming officials of corruption.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:54.66,1:45:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你在我的旅館接受招待 並答應我會有公平的聽證會\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}...promised me a fair hearing when you were comped at my hotel?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:57.66,1:46:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你還要求將你的帳單掛公帳\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}And you asked for copies of your bill to put on your expense account.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:01.00,1:46:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,當賭博遊樂執照被駁回時大吼大叫…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}In a wild outburst that followed his gaming license denial...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:04.38,1:46:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-狗屁！ -羅斯坦與好幾名…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Bullshit! ...Rothstein followed several...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:06.71,1:46:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,錯愕的委員到走道 並持續著他的指控…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}stunned commissioners into the hallway where he continued his harangue...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:10.26,1:46:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,直到他的律師與朋友勸他離開\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}until his own lawyers and friends urged him to leave.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:12.89,1:46:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你有過去，我也有過去 我的不見得比你的糟糕\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You have a past. I have a past. My past is no worse than yours.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.14,1:46:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你們還自以為有權去判決別人！\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You guys think you have the right to pass judgment!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:20.02,1:46:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,被懷疑長期無照管理坦吉樂…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NEWSREADER: Long suspected of running Tangiers without a license...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:23.23,1:46:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天的聽證會本是要決議 像羅斯坦如此背景的人…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}yesterday's hearing was to determine if someone with Rothstein's history...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:27.82,1:46:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是否有資格正式在賭博遊樂界 擔任如此高的職位\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}was qualified to officially hold a top gaming post.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:30.78,1:46:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,羅斯坦玩完了 王八偽君子！\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}REMO: Fucking hypocrites!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:33.53,1:46:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,-他現在怎麼辦？ -我不知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-What the hell's he gonna do now? -I don't know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:37.12,1:46:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,他在幹嘛？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}What's he doing?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:38.87,1:46:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他也知道他大吼大叫的那群人 都是我們的朋友\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He knows all those guys he yelled at are friends of ours.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:41.79,1:46:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他是怎麼了，搞得一團糟？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}What's the matter with him, making all this mess?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:44.13,1:46:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他或許可以用另一個頭銜管事\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Maybe he could run things with another job title.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:46.63,1:46:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是最好的 但我們又能如何呢？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Won't be the best, but what are we gonna do?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:49.34,1:46:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他不論管什麼，都得安靜點\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}REMO: However he runs things, it's gotta be quiet.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:51.34,1:46:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,讓他躲到樓上辦公室去\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Let him hide upstairs in the office.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:53.72,1:46:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,說他是工友，我不在乎\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Say he's a janitor. I don't give a shit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:55.97,1:47:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,但拜託，不管他做什麼 都得低調點\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}But please, whatever job he takes, make sure it's something quiet.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:09.91,1:47:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,各位先生與女士…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}ANNOUNCER: [On TV] Ladies and gentlemen...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:11.37,1:47:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,坦吉樂大飯店 非常榮幸能為您介紹…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}the Tangiers Hotel proudly presents the all-new...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:14.33,1:47:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,山姆羅斯坦秀，   《艾斯的單人牌》\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Sam Rothstein show, Aces High.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:17.16,1:47:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,艾斯的單人牌
Dialogue: 0,1:47:20.96,1:47:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚，從最新的球賽賭區 現場實況轉播…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Tonight, taped live from the all-new sports book...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:23.92,1:47:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我們為您帶來《艾斯的單人牌》的 首次演出…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}we present the premiere showing of Aces High...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.05,1:47:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,連同莎夏西門諾夫交響樂團…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}with the Sasha Semenoff Orchestra...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:30.84,1:47:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,與山姆羅斯坦舞群！\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}and the Sam Rothstein dancers!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:35.18,1:47:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,羅斯坦先生是位職業賭徒 也是全美最棒的美式足球下注者\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Mr. Rothstein is a professional gambler and the best U.S. football handicapper.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:40.23,1:47:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,一位能帶領你進入 真正的拉斯維加斯的人\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}A man who will take you inside the real Las Vegas as no one has ever done before.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:45.36,1:47:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,現在讓我們歡迎 坦吉樂賭場新的娛樂董事…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Now, the new entertainment director of the Tangiers Hotel Casino...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.91,1:47:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,山姆羅斯坦先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Mr. Sam Rothstein.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:01.00,1:48:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎來到山姆羅斯坦秀 很高興你們能參與\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Welcome to the Sam Rothstein show. We're happy to have you here this evening.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:05.51,1:48:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我左邊的這位小姐是特茹蒂…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}The young lady to my left is Trudy...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:08.47,1:48:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,她是我們巴黎秀新的首席舞者\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}who is a lead new dancer in our fabulous show from Paris.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:11.85,1:48:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我們今晚的第一位來寶…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Our first guest this evening...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:15.56,1:48:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,法蘭克艾華倫\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}is Frankie Avalon.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:22.82,1:48:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,-看好他 -我有個大家庭\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}PAT: Keep an eye on him. FRANKIE: I've got a large family.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:26.28,1:48:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-你有幾個孩子？ -我很自豪的說，八個\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: How many kids do you have? I'm very proud to say, eight children.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:34.00,1:48:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-太了不起了 -沒什麼，是我的榮幸\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-That's amazing. -There's nothing to it. It was my pleasure.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.38,1:48:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,別這樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}PHILIP: Ace, don't do it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:45.51,1:48:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Jesus.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:47.43,1:48:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他在耍雜技！\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He's juggling!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:49.18,1:48:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我們別對縣輔導 派特委布太認真\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Let's not take County Commissioner Pat Webb too seriously.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:53.18,1:48:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我最近本想邀他在節目上辯論的 但是他拒絕了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I recently challenged him to a debate on this program, and he declined.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:56.94,1:48:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你在擔心什麼呢，派特？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}What are you worried about, Pat?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:59.03,1:49:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你不需要事先給我問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You don't have to send me any questions.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:02.19,1:49:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你什麼都可以問我\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You can ask me anything you want.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:04.32,1:49:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他在電視上幹嘛？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}ANDY: What the hell is he doing on television?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:06.70,1:49:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他整晚都在上面\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He's on all night,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:07.75,1:49:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,喊著要將他的案子告上最高法院\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}screaming about taking his lawsuit to the Supreme Court.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:12.58,1:49:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他真是瘋了 他想將這帶到華府去？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He really must be crazy. He's gonna go to Washington with this?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:16.63,1:49:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他簡直是瘋了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He's out of his fucking mind.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:18.21,1:49:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,世上有這樣的偽君子真是可歎 他們愛做什麼就做什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}It's a pity we have such hypocrisy. Some people do what they want.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:22.13,1:49:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,其他人卻得承擔後果 這就是人生\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Other people have to pay through the nose. Such is life.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:25.26,1:49:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,安迪，去找他 告訴他辭職的時候到了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Andy, go see him. Tell him maybe it's time he should quit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:36.27,1:49:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,第一點，他們的所做所為 完全的違反了憲法\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: First, what they did was totally unconstitutional.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:39.15,1:49:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我們已在高等法院的等候單上了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: We're on the list to be heard before the U.S. Supreme Court.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:42.90,1:49:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,這些傢伙才不在乎高等法院\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}These guys don't care about the Supreme Court.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:45.32,1:49:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他們要一切平息，要你別再搞了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}They want things to quiet down. They want you to walk away.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:47.80,1:49:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,別搞了？安迪，\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Walk away? Andy,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:48.61,1:49:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是說真的 你難道看不到這嚴重性嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}you can't be serious. Don't you see what's at stake?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:53.33,1:49:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,老頭說你的朋友或許該罷手了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}The old man said maybe your friend should give in.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:56.34,1:49:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,當老頭說“或許”時 就像是教皇發諭令一樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}When the old man says "maybe," that's like a papal bull.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:59.30,1:50:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你不但該罷手，還該跑路\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Not only should you quit, you should run.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:02.17,1:50:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他們每次在報上提到我的名字 就一定扯到尼奇\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Every time they mention my name in the papers, they mention Nicky, too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:06.68,1:50:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,這他媽的有什麼幫助？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}How the fuck does that help?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:09.35,1:50:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他帶來的注目簡直是謀殺\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}The heat he brought down is murder.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:11.64,1:50:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,警察局本來很合作\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}The police department was cooperative.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:13.69,1:50:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他將他們激怒到 現在大家都動不了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}They're pissed off. Nobody can make a move anymore.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:16.48,1:50:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你能怎樣呢？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}What do you do about that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:17.86,1:50:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-你想說什麼？ -我不知道，他根本不聽我的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-What are you proposing? -I don't know. He doesn't listen to me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:21.15,1:50:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,或許他才該消失一陣子 這樣會很糟嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Maybe he should get lost for a while. Would that be so bad?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:23.95,1:50:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,-他們不會調走尼奇的 -若他離開一陣…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-They ain't sending Nicky nowhere. -If he took a break...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:26.62,1:50:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,給大家移動佈局的機會\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}it would give everybody time to maneuver.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:28.87,1:50:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,別再搞佈局的事 趕緊離開吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I would forget about the maneuver. I would just get out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:36.88,1:50:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I can't do that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:39.21,1:50:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,當然，安迪一到家後 尼奇就聽說我們的談話\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Of course, as soon as Andy got home, Nicky heard about our talk in the car.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:43.64,1:50:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,第二天一大早，我就接到電話\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Next morning, bright and early, I get the call.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:47.47,1:50:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我得去買點東西，你要不要去？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I've got to do some shopping. Want to go?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:49.89,1:50:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,連接尼奇的電話都不是件易事\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Getting a call from Nicky wasn't easy anymore.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:52.56,1:50:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,暗號都沒有用了 我們得想新方法\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Even the codes didn't work. So we figured out another act.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:55.08,1:50:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,若是電話被竊聽\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}If a phone's tapped,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:56.64,1:50:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,他們只能聽關於犯罪的談話\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}the Feds can only listen in on the stuff involving crimes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:00.07,1:51:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,例行通話時 他們必須在幾分鐘後掛斷\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}On routine calls, they have to click off after a few minutes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:03.66,1:51:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我手肘好像扭到了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}GINGER: I got a sprained fucking elbow.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:06.87,1:51:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,三點見\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Meet me at 3:00.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:08.25,1:51:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,-在凱撒宮嗎？ -這條路下去再一百碼處\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-At Caesar's? -100 yards further down the road.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:11.58,1:51:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-為什麼？ -別問了，到那兒就是了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-Why? -Don't ask questions. Just be there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:16.13,1:51:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,蘇西克理姆有件一模一樣的衣服\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Suzy Cream Cheese has the same outfit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:20.59,1:51:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到個東西\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}GINGER: I saw something.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:22.09,1:51:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,這東西好可愛\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Something very cute.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:25.26,1:51:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他出門了，棕組\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}AGENT: Okay, he's out. It's the ant. Brown unit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:29.27,1:51:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他帶著個替身，應該是法蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He's with the bogey. I think it's Frankie.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:32.19,1:51:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,尼奇比我早出門…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Nicky started out before me...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:34.19,1:51:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,因為他要出門越來越難了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}because it wasn't that easy for him to get around anymore.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:38.65,1:51:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,尼奇到那兒都最起碼得…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Nicky couldn't even go for a ride without changing cars...{\r}
