Dialogue: 0,1:59:34.99,1:59:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到任何跡象 讓你覺得…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Do you see anything that makes you think I would ever let...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:59:38.24,1:59:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,以你現在的狀況 我會將我的孩子交給你？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}someone in your condition take my child away from me?{\r}
