Dialogue: 0,1:59:54.01,1:59:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,過了這麼久…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: And after all this time...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:59:56.05,1:59:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不管我多麼努力，多麼想…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}and as hard as I tried, as much as I wanted...{\r}
