Dialogue: 0,2:00:20.37,2:00:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那時，我記得金吉兒 帶著艾美去比佛利山莊\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}At that time, I remember Ginger took Amy and went to Beverly Hills.{\r}
