Dialogue: 0,2:00:32.46,2:00:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉，羅斯坦先生與夫人 已經退房了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}RECEPTIONIST: Sorry, Mr. and Mrs. Rothstein have checked out already.{\r}
