Dialogue: 0,2:00:57.74,2:01:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我女兒跟他們在一起 他們會試著綁架她\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}My daughter's with them. They're gonna try and kidnap her.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:00.66,2:01:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,-你那邊有人嗎？ -我們會幫你搞定\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Is there anybody you can send? MAN: We'll take care of it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:09.46,2:01:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,查到電話號碼與住址了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}We got a number and an address.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:11.17,2:01:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，是萊斯特嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Hello. Is this Lester?{\r}
