Dialogue: 0,2:01:16.93,2:01:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我是山姆羅斯坦 我要跟金吉兒講話\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}This is Sam Rothstein. I want to talk to Ginger.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:20.47,2:01:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,她不在這兒，山姆\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}She's not here, Sam.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:22.18,2:01:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你給我聽好 我要跟金吉兒說話\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Listen to me very carefully. I want to talk to Ginger.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:25.27,2:01:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我要我的孩子 我要她馬上搭下班飛機回來\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I want my kid back. I want her put on a plane immediately.{\r}
