Dialogue: 0,2:01:52.63,2:01:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,白癡，好了 我多拖了一些時間\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Schmuck. All right, I just bought us a few minutes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:56.42,2:01:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你想報復嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}LESTER: You want to get back at this prick?{\r}
