Dialogue: 0,2:02:02.39,2:02:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，耽誤你一下？ 他保險箱埵釣潀妐U對吧？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You got a minute? He's got $2 million in the box, right?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:05.98,2:02:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,珠寶就留給他，我們拿走現金…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You let him keep your jewels. We take the cash...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:08.56,2:02:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,與他唯一在乎的另一件東西 他的小公主\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}and the only other thing he cares about. Her majesty.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:11.40,2:02:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我們去歐洲，你把頭髮染了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}We go to Europe. You dye your hair.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:13.98,2:02:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要去歐洲 我要去看TheEIephantMan\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I don't want to go to Europe. I want to go to see The Elephant Man.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:18.03,2:02:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我們要去歐洲，讓大人講話 你去染頭髮\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}We're going to Europe. Let the adults talk. You dye your hair.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:21.87,2:02:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,像我們所說的去整容\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You get plastic surgery like we talked about.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:24.37,2:02:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得他會願意付多少贖金？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}How much you think he'll pay to get this kid back?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:27.04,2:02:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-我不要去歐洲 -你給我閉嘴\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}AMY: I don't want to go to Europe. LESTER: Shut your mouth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:29.83,2:02:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,-你才閉嘴 -你要我過來？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}AMY: You shut up. LESTER: Want me to come over?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:32.00,2:02:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我一巴掌打死你，別找我麻煩！\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}LESTER: I'll smack your face. Don't give me your shit!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:34.55,2:02:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,這本來是個夢 但現在要實現了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}This has always been a dream, but now we're going.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:37.09,2:02:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,-萊斯特，他打到這兒來 -他剛在電話上\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-Lester, he called you here. -Right. Ace was on the phone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:40.93,2:02:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-我剛跟他講完 -所以他知道你在哪兒\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-I just talked to him. -So he knows where you are.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:43.22,2:02:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,這表示他現在就派人過來了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}That means he's sending some guys over here now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:45.60,2:02:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,這表示他在電話旁像個蠢蛋…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}It means he's sitting by the phone, like a dumbbell....{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:48.85,2:02:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,對，他就像是蠢蛋坐在電話旁 等你打給他！\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}GINGER: Yeah, he's sitting by the phone waiting for you to call him back!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:52.56,2:02:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我們該怎麼辦？他可能 已經派人在門外守著了！\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}What are we gonna do? He's probably got guys outside the fucking house!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:56.57,2:02:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,-又是你在那兒鬼扯！ -快拿行李，快走！\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-It's this fucking bullshit of yours! -Get your bag! Let's go!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:00.78,2:03:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-什麼鬼扯？你想現在討論這嗎？ -你嘮叨完了沒？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-What bullshit? You want to talk it over? -Are you done yakking?{\r}
