Dialogue: 0,2:03:09.79,2:03:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,-他一定會殺了我 -冷靜點\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}GINGER: I think he's gonna kill me. NICKY: Relax.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:11.67,2:03:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,一個小時後打這支電話給我 我想想辦法\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Call me back here in exactly an hour on this phone. I'll see what I can do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:16.17,2:03:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我一個小時後打給你…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I'll call you back in an hour at this number...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:18.84,2:03:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,-你會接對不對？ -我會在\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-and you'll be there, right? -I'll be here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:20.80,2:03:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,聽著，別再做什麼蠢事了 你還好嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Listen, don't do anything else crazy. You all right?{\r}
