Dialogue: 0,2:03:30.89,2:03:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,-你別想開車 -我來開\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-Don't even think you're gonna drive. -I'm gonna drive.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:33.48,2:03:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-我可不想坐瘋婆子開的車 -你快把我搞瘋了！\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}LESTER: I'm not gonna drive with a crazy woman. You're driving me nuts!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:36.61,2:03:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,滾到旁邊去！ 我要將這小鬼裝箱寄到玻利維亞去！\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Get on the passenger side! I'm sending this kid to Bolivia in a box!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:56.84,2:03:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我們能不能…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Can we....{\r}
