Dialogue: 0,2:04:37.59,2:04:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他們想綁架我的孩子 你覺得我會怎樣？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}They're gonna kidnap my kid. What do you want?{\r}
