Dialogue: 0,2:38:02.27,2:38:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是需要領一些現金 你可以陪我來嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}GINGER: I just need to pick up a little cash. Could you come with me?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:38:12.19,2:38:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-你得阻止她 -抱歉，山姆\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: You've got to stop her. CHARLIE: I'm sorry, Sam.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:38:15.61,2:38:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-我無能為力 -她是個毒蟲，根本就瘋了！\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}CHARLIE: What can I do? SAM: She's a junkie. She's out of her mind!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:38:18.83,2:38:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,她有鑰匙，而且你們兩人名字 都在戶頭上\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}She has the keys. It's still in both your names.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:38:21.20,2:38:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我無能為力，我想要幫忙…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}There's nothing I can do. I'd like to help...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:38:24.12,2:38:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-但我不能 -嚴格說，她不能拿\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-but I can't. -Legally, she can't take it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:38:26.21,2:38:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,-她不能，一半是我的 -聽我說\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: She can't. Half of it is mine. CHARLIE: Listen to me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:38:28.96,2:38:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-我愛莫能助 -我馬上到\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}CHARLIE: There's nothing I can do. SAM: I'm coming down.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:38:44.68,2:38:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,媽的！靠！\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Shit! God damn it!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:38:48.06,2:38:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要個袋子 你可以幫我要個袋子嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I'll need a bag. Could you ask the guy for the big bag?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:38:51.98,2:38:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,-拿個袋吧 -拿去\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}COP: Go get a bag, man. GINGER: Here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:38:54.32,2:38:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,-小姐，我不能拿 -你可以，你對我好好\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-Lady, I can't take it. -You can. You've been so nice to me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:38:58.99,2:39:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好，幫我打開，好嗎？ 這樣我就可以…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}GINGER: Yes, just hold the top open. All right? And I can....{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:39:06.21,2:39:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊，是他！ 你們得阻止他\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, God! It's him. You have to stop him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:39:09.00,2:39:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,因為他說他會殺了我\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}'Cause he said he was gonna kill me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:39:12.67,2:39:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,羅斯坦先生，等一下\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}COP: Mr. Rothstein, wait a minute.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:39:15.76,2:39:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,請等一下\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}COP: Hold on a second.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:39:17.76,2:39:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-她開走了 -我們不能做什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: She's driving away. COP: There's nothing we can do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:39:21.18,2:39:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,-我們不能做什麼 -你瞧瞧\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-There's nothing we can do. -Look, look.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:39:23.77,2:39:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你們不能抓她超速嗎？ 看看她開多快\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You can't stop her for speeding? Look what she's doing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:39:27.27,2:39:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-我們不能做什麼，她有鑰匙 -她的名字在戶頭上\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}COP: Nothing we can do. She had the key. COP 2: She's on the account.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:39:31.11,2:39:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-我們在加油站攔她 -好的，就這麼辦\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-Let's pull her over at that Citgo Station. -Okay. Let's do it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:39:45.87,2:39:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-我們必須逮捕你 -為了什麼？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-We're placing you under arrest. -For what?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:39:48.79,2:39:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-為了協助犯罪… -為了什麼？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-For aiding and abetting-- -For what?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:39:52.04,2:39:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-為了協助犯罪… -我只是要離開\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-For aiding and abetting-- -I'm just trying to leave.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:39:55.59,2:39:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,在這麼多威脅之後…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: After all the threats and bullshit...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:39:57.68,2:39:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,金吉兒什麼都沒告訴他們\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}it turned out Ginger didn't tell them anything.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:39:59.80,2:40:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,但那時，他們也不需要她了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}But, by then, the Feds didn't need her anyway.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:40:03.43,2:40:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,-他們已有足夠的證據 -但我什麼都沒做\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}They had all the pieces they needed. But I didn't do anything.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:40:06.52,2:40:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,-大家就像牌九一樣跟著倒 -聯邦調查局！我們有拘捕令！\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Everyone began to tumble, like dominoes. FBI! We have a warrant!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:40:11.90,2:40:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不管是竊聽器上派斯康的抱怨…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Between Piscano complaining on the wire...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:40:14.40,2:40:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,還是尼奇、我與我的執照…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}between Nicky, Ginger, me and my license...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:40:17.74,2:40:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,天堂就這樣被我們搞砸了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}paradise. We managed to really fuck it up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:40:21.57,2:40:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,-媽 -門口他媽的有人\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY JR.: Mom. JENNIFER: Someone's at the door now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:40:24.95,2:40:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,聯邦調查局，我們有搜查令\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}FBI. We have a federal search warrant.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:40:27.25,2:40:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我馬上知道苗頭不對 所以我跑路了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: I got wind of the pinches coming down, so I took off.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:40:30.42,2:40:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,誰要待在那兒找麻煩啊？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Who needs to hang around for that bullshit?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:40:32.46,2:40:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-我是馬克凱斯伯，FBI -是嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-I'm Mark Casper, FBI. -Yeah?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:40:34.75,2:40:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以打個電話嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Can I make a fucking phone call?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:40:36.42,2:40:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,可以，但你不用這樣對我們講話\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, but you don't have to talk to us like that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:40:39.01,2:40:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都出去 往警鈴的方向走\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}FBI AGENT: Everybody, out of the room. Over to the alarm.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:40:42.10,2:40:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-其他人似乎都被抓了 -這地方被查封了！\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: They got almost everybody else. FBI AGENT: This area is seized!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:40:45.93,2:40:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,-去拿總戶頭單 -我要查封所有的檔\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-Get the master account list. -I want all those papers seized.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:40:53.44,2:40:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,將每個箱子都放到桌上\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}FBI AGENT: Put every box on the table.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:41:02.49,2:41:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好，在這兒，所有的數字\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Yes. Here we are. Little craps figures.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:41:06.24,2:41:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,葛林？別提了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Green? Don't even ask.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:41:07.87,2:41:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-你的三萬元 -不，所以不成立\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-...$30,000 of yours. -No. That's why it wasn't valid.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:41:10.75,2:41:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我是被敲詐的 你們想知道什麼就問我\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I was being extorted. I'll tell you what you want to know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:41:14.09,2:41:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-我不需要隱藏 -最經典的是\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}PHlLlP: I've got nothing to hide. NICKY: Now for the best.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:41:16.21,2:41:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我不敢相信派斯康的花費記錄 竟然成了關鍵\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I couldn't believe this shit. Piscano's expense reports took the cake.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:41:20.72,2:41:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-這太好了 -他乾脆就把藍圖給他們算了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, this is good. NICKY: He might as well give them a blueprint.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:41:24.18,2:41:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人的名字、地址、日期 一切都在上面\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Everybody's names, addresses, dates, everything.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:41:27.81,2:41:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,真是多謝你了，派斯康先生 你真是體帖\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Thank you so much, Mr. Piscano. How considerate of you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:41:31.31,2:41:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-那是我媽的賬目 -你被逮捕了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-Those are my mother's books. -You're under arrest.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:41:34.15,2:41:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,-真是個蠢才 -你在幹嘛？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: What a fucking balloon head. ARTIE: What are you doing?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:41:36.78,2:41:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-冷靜點 -等一下！\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}AGENT: Take it easy. WIFE: Wait!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:41:39.11,2:41:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,-等一下，他有病！ -走開\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}WIFE: Wait! He's sick! COP: Move back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:41:41.24,2:41:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,-是心臟，還呼吸嗎？ -快人工呼吸！\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}WIFE: It's his heart! Is he breathing? COP 2: CPR now!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:41:43.70,2:41:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,艾提被搞到心臟病發…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Artie got so upset he had a heart attack...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:41:45.83,2:41:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,當他老婆的面就掛了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}and dropped dead right in front of his wife.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:41:48.25,2:41:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-冷靜點！ -我無法冷靜！\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-Calm down! -No, I won't calm down!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:41:50.21,2:41:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,-他是我丈夫，艾提！ -我們也不能…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-He's my husband! Artie! -We can't help him if--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:41:56.38,2:41:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,最後…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: At the end of the day...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:41:57.84,2:42:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他們終於拿照片來給我看\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}they finally came to see me with the pictures.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:42:00.42,2:42:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼要保護一個背叛你的朋友？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}FBI AGENT: Why protect a friend who betrayed you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:42:03.09,2:42:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,但我並不想看它們…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: But I didn't want to look at them...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:42:05.10,2:42:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,或是拿照片來的人\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}or the guys who brought them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:42:10.27,2:42:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,大人，你可看見，\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}COUNSELOR: Your Honor, as you can see,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:42:11.51,2:42:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我的客戶們 都年事已大並生病\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}my clients are elderly and infirm.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:42:13.85,2:42:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,任何的刑責都將會 嚴重威脅到他們的健康\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}COUNSELOR: Any incarceration could pose a serious health risk.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:42:17.11,2:42:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,當老大們被逮時 有些簡直老到…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: When they were arrested, some were so old...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:42:19.44,2:42:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,罪狀認否程式時都需要醫師\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}they needed doctors at their arraignment.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:42:21.36,2:42:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,預審時建議將保釋金額 維持現額\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}COUNSELOR: Pre-trial services recommends that bail remain as set.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:42:24.53,2:42:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,-現在休庭 -當情況看來他們似乎…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}JUDGE: Take recess. NICKY: When it looked like they'd get...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:42:27.33,2:42:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,得為了抽頭而關上25年時…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}25 years to life in prison just for skimming a casino...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:42:30.37,2:42:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不管有病沒病 總有人要倒楣\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}sick or no fucking sick, you knew people were going to get clipped.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:42:34.92,2:42:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,所以在罪狀認否程式那天\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}So the day of the arraignment,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:42:36.62,2:42:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他們在法庭後頭開會\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}they had this meeting in the back of the courthouse.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:42:39.34,2:42:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,當類似的事發生時\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}When something like this happens,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:42:41.38,2:42:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你已知道事情會怎樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}you know how things are gonna work out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:42:43.55,2:42:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,最好是不要有目擊者 那安迪呢？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}It's always better with no witnesses. So what about Andy?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:42:47.93,2:42:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他不會說的，史東是好傢伙\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He won't talk. Stone is a good kid.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:42:51.06,2:42:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,跟他老爸一樣帶種\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Stand-up guy just like his old man.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:42:53.48,2:42:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我是這麼想的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}That's the way I see it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:42:55.23,2:42:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我同意，他很強悍\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I agree. He's solid. He's a fucking Marine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:42:59.36,2:43:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他沒問題，一直都是 你說呢？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He's okay. He always was. What do you think?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:43:05.16,2:43:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼要冒險呢？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Look, why take a chance?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:43:11.29,2:43:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我是這麼想的啦\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}At least that's the way I feel about it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:43:14.25,2:43:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,打給艾提，告訴他不管怎樣…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}ANDY: Call Artie. Tell him I don't care what...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:43:17.59,2:43:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他星期四都得來我辦公室\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}he's gotta be in my office Thursday morning.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:43:19.75,2:43:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,決定了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}It's done.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:43:20.88,2:43:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,非常重要 我一定得跟他談談\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}It's terribly important. I gotta have a conversation with him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:43:32.14,2:43:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不管他們多喜歡他 他還不是家族一員\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: As much as they liked him, he wasn't one of us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:43:34.94,2:43:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,他不是義大利人 對他們來說，他隨時可能供出來\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He wasn't Italian. As far as they knew, he could have talked.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:43:38.32,2:43:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,要不然他可能還活著\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Otherwise, he'd still be alive.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:43:41.61,2:43:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,哥斯大黎加
Dialogue: 0,2:43:45.16,2:43:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,第一個翹頭的就是約翰南斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}The first one to skip was John Nance.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:43:47.57,2:43:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他在哥斯大黎加 找了個又好又隱密的地方\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He found a nice, warm, secluded place in Costa Rica.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:43:50.83,2:43:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,他以為沒人找得到他\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He thought nobody would find him there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:44:14.18,2:44:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但他孩子隨後因犯毒 被聯邦調查局逮了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: But then his kid got nabbed by the Feds for drugs.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:44:17.23,2:44:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,老大們當然怕他會出現…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}So naturally, the bosses were afraid he'd come out of hiding...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:44:20.44,2:44:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,為了救孩子而把大家供出來\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}just to save his kid and give them all up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:44:23.57,2:44:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,所以…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}So....{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:44:27.57,2:44:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你想去哪里？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Where you going, jag-off?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:44:31.29,2:44:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但大家都得跟著\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: But, anyway, they all had to follow.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:44:33.54,2:44:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都完了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Everybody went down.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:44:35.08,2:44:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,去你的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Fuck you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:44:42.05,2:44:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不知不覺…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: Before you knew it...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:44:43.34,2:44:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,任何知道一點小事的人 都被幹掉了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}anybody who knew anything wound up getting whacked.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:44:54.73,2:44:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不！不！\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}GINGER: Oh, no! No!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:45:02.07,2:45:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,金吉兒走後 她對任何人都沒什麼用\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: After Ginger took off, she wasn't much help to anybody.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:45:04.74,2:45:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,她在洛杉磯結識了一些 皮條客、敗類、毒蟲與飛車黨\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}She found some pimps, lowlifes, druggies, and bikers in L.A.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:45:08.74,2:45:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,幾個月內，他們就把 所有的錢跟珠寶花光了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}In a few months, they went through all the money and jewels.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:45:38.14,2:45:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,當他們找到遺體時…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}After they found her body...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:45:40.56,2:45:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我私下請了個醫生驗屍\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I had a private doctor do another autopsy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:45:46.61,2:45:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他說他們給她打了過量的毒品\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He said they gave her a hot dose.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:45:49.49,2:45:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,最終，她身上只剩下 價值三千六百元的全新硬幣\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}In the end, all she had left was $3, 600 in mint condition coins.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:46:16.10,2:46:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不管條子與檔 對我的汽車炸彈有什麼評論…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}No matter what the Feds or the papers said about my car bombing...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:46:21.69,2:46:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,一看就知道是新手幹的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}it was amateur night, you could tell.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:46:23.94,2:46:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不管是誰，他們將炸彈裝在 副駕駛座下面\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Whoever it was, they put the dynamite under the passenger side.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:46:27.74,2:46:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他們不知道的是 除了車廠外沒人知道的是…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}But what they didn't know, what nobody outside the factory knew...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:46:31.66,2:46:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那台車的駕駛座下 多加了一塊鐵板\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}was that, that model car was made with a metal plate under the driver's seat.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:46:36.87,2:46:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,全靠了它救我一命\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}It's the only thing that saved my life.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:46:51.76,2:46:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那炸彈從沒被批准 但我想我知道是誰幹的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}The bombing was never authorized, but I suspect I know who lit the fuse.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:46:57.39,2:46:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,老大們也知道吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}So did the powers that be.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:46:59.44,2:47:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-你好嗎？ -你好嗎？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: How are you? BOSS: How you doing?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:47:01.23,2:47:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好幾個月後一切才平息\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: It took months for everything to calm down.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:47:03.56,2:47:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但我的人終於保釋出來了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}But finally, my guys got out on bail.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:47:06.03,2:47:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,老大們要我將我小弟 多明尼送回賭城\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}The bosses wanted me to send my brother Dominick out to Vegas.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:47:09.65,2:47:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,永遠都是為了錢\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Always the fucking dollars.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:47:13.07,2:47:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我是說，我連賭城都不能踏入\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I mean, it was still too hot for me to even go near Vegas.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:47:16.74,2:47:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我在個鳥不生蛋的地方 安排大家碰面\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}So I set up a meeting with the guys way out in the sticks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:47:19.50,2:47:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想害我小弟 對的就是對的\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I didn't want my brother to get fucked around. What's right is right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:47:22.83,2:47:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他們才不在乎…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}They don't give a fuck about--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:47:26.05,2:47:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,去你媽的…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}THUG: Holy fucking....{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:47:28.51,2:47:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什麼…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: What the fuck....{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:47:29.92,2:47:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,來啊，王八蛋！\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Come on, motherfucker!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:47:32.97,2:47:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不是很猛嗎？你跟你哥！\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Tough guys! You and your fucking brother!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:47:36.26,2:47:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你們兩個渾蛋！夠了！\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You fucking scumbags! No more!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:47:42.31,2:47:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-法蘭克！ -夠了！你看著！\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-Frankie! -No more! You see? Watch!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:47:48.90,2:47:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-法蘭克！你這王八蛋！ -去你的！\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: Frankie! You piece of shit! FRANK: Fuck you!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:47:53.49,2:47:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,王八羔子！狗雜種！\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: Fucking punk! Piece of shit!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:48:00.04,2:48:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不！\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}No!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:48:01.87,2:48:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,把這渾蛋拖走！\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Take this motherfucker out!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:48:11.55,2:48:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,別搞他了，他還活著
Dialogue: 0,2:48:14.64,2:48:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他還在呼吸 別搞他了，法蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He's still breathing. Leave him alone. Frankie.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:48:22.52,2:48:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，脫他衣服\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}FRANK: All right. Strip him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:48:25.69,2:48:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,沒種，你真他媽的沒種\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: No balls. You got no fucking balls.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:48:29.32,2:48:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,多明尼！\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, Dominick!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:48:38.45,2:48:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,多明尼\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: Dominick.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:49:03.64,2:49:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}FRANK: Come on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:49:08.32,2:49:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,-埋了他們？ -埋\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}THUG: Bury them? FRANK: Bury them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:49:13.40,2:49:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,話放出去了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: The word was out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:49:14.53,2:49:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,老大們受夠了尼奇 受夠了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}The bosses had enough of Nicky. They had enough.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:49:17.45,2:49:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他們還能忍受多久呢？ 所以拿他們兄弟倆殺雞儆猴\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}How much were they gonna take? So they made an example of him and his brother.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:49:23.16,2:49:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他們倆被活埋\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}They buried them while they were still breathing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:49:43.18,2:49:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你還好嗎？小心！\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}MAN: You all right? Watch out!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:49:50.86,2:49:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-先生，你沒事吧？ -沒事\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}MAN: Mister, you all right? SAM: Yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:49:54.90,2:49:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他們有別的事給我做\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: They had other ideas for me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:50:06.62,2:50:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我們這兒需要幫忙！\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}MEDIC: We need some help over here!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:50:10.50,2:50:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你真是幸運\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}MEDIC 2: You sure are lucky, mister.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:50:30.44,2:50:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,這城市再也不一樣了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: The town will never be the same.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:50:33.15,2:50:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,在坦吉樂之後，大集團全權掌管\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}After the Tangiers, the big corporations took it all over.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:50:37.82,2:50:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,今日的賭城像是迪斯奈樂園\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Today it looks like Disneyland.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:50:47.67,2:50:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子們玩著海盜遊戲時…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}While the kids play cardboard pirates...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:50:49.84,2:50:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸與媽媽將房貸與大學學費…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Mommy and Daddy drop the house payments and junior's college money...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:50:53.34,2:50:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,浪費在吃角子老虎機\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}on the poker slots.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:50:59.43,2:51:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,想當年，莊家知道你的名字 喝什麼酒，玩什麼牌\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}In the old days, dealers knew your name, what you drank, what you played.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:51:03.06,2:51:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,今天就像是在機場登記一般\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Today, it's like checking into an airport.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:51:05.27,2:51:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是叫客房送餐 星期四給你送到就了不起了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}If you order room service, you're lucky if you get it by Thursday.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:51:09.81,2:51:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,都沒了，一個人拎著 裝著四百萬的皮箱…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Today it's all gone. A whale shows up with $4 million in a suitcase...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:51:13.28,2:51:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,就有個25歲的旅遊系大學畢業生 想要他的身份字型大小\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}and some 25-year-old hotel school kid will want his Social Security number.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:51:19.74,2:51:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,全美卡車司機工會離開後…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}After the Teamsters got knocked out of the box...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:51:21.99,2:51:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,大集團幾乎將所有的舊賭場都拆了\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}the corporations tore down practically every one of the old casinos.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:51:26.33,2:51:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,而蓋新金字塔的錢是從哪來的呢？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}And where did the money come from to rebuild the pyramids?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:51:30.25,2:51:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,垃圾債券\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Junk bonds.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:51:33.21,2:51:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,聖地牙哥
Dialogue: 0,2:51:37.22,2:51:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,還不確定？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Still not sure?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:51:39.43,2:51:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,有可能，有些質疑\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Probable. Maybe questionable.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:51:41.39,2:51:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，知道後立即通知我\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: All right, let me know as soon as you can find out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:51:45.27,2:51:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,最後，我又回到了起點\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: In the end, I wound up right back where I started.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:51:48.48,2:51:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我還是會選贏家…\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I could still pick winners...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:51:50.40,2:51:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,也還是可以為老家 各式各樣的人賺錢\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}and I could still make money for all kinds of people back home.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:51:53.86,2:51:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,何必搞砸好事呢？\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}And why mess up a good thing?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:51:56.95,2:51:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這樣！\N{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}And that's that!{\r}

